Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:55.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}1957年10月 苏联将\N{\rOriginal text}In October 1957, the Soviet Union launched
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:59.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}世界上第一颗人造卫星 斯普特尼克1号送入轨道\N{\rOriginal text}the world's first artificial satellite, Sputnik 1, into orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:04.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这一成就加剧了美苏两国之间的太空竞赛\N{\rOriginal text}Their achievement fueled a space race between the United States and the Soviets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:07.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}之后发生了什么 人们说法不一\N{\rOriginal text}There has been some debate about what followed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:12.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我亲身经历过 所以接下来讲的都是真事 基本上是吧\N{\rOriginal text}but I was there, and this is the real story. Mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}直到两天前\N{\rOriginal text}Until two days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:16.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}地球上的人才头一次听到这个声音\N{\rOriginal text}that sound had never been heard on this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:19.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(苏联人将卫星送进太空)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:22.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(《生活》 太空竞赛)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:26.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(美国卫星一败涂地)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}美国尝试发射自己的卫星 结果惨不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:31.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(美国火箭计划启动失败)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}苏联成功地将一个人送入太空\N{\rOriginal text}The Soviet Union has sent a man into space
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(第一个进入太空的人)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:36.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}并把他活着带回地球\N{\rOriginal text}and brought him back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:38.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}苏联人在全世界范围内\N{\rOriginal text}The Soviets made the most of the flight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:41.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大肆宣传这次航天行动 其国内自然也是举国欢庆\N{\rOriginal text}in their worldwide propaganda. Naturally, there was jubilation in Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在认识到苏联人取得领先后\N{\rOriginal text}Recognizing the head start obtained by the Soviets,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:51.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我认为我国应致力于实现一个目标\N{\rOriginal text}I believe that this nation should commit itself to achieving the goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}即在这个十年内\N{\rOriginal text}before this decade is out,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:57.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}把一个人送上月球并让他安全返回地球\N{\rOriginal text}of landing a man on the moon and returning him safely to the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(美国宇航员环绕地球飞行)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:15.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们选择在这个十年登月\N{\rOriginal text}We choose to go to the moon in this decade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:18.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}并完成其他壮举 不是因为这个目标轻而易举\N{\rOriginal text}and do the other things, not because they are easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而是因为它困难重重\N{\rOriginal text}but because they are hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:23.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为这个挑战是我们愿意接受\N{\rOriginal text}Because that challenge is one that we are willing to accept,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:26.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不愿推迟 并准备大获全胜的\N{\rOriginal text}one we are unwilling to postpone, and one we intend to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}指挥飞行员 一 二 三 四 五\N{\rOriginal text}Command Pilot. One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}五 四 三 二 一\N{\rOriginal text}Five, four, three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:32.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}着火了\N{\rOriginal text}Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:34.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}驾驶舱里失火了\N{\rOriginal text}We've got a fire in the cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}快出去 我们要烧死了\N{\rOriginal text}Let's get out! We're burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:42.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}宇航员维吉尔·格里森 爱德华·怀特 和罗杰·查菲不幸遇难\N{\rOriginal text}Astronauts Virgil Grissom, Edward White and Roger Chaffee have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}媒体官员称 因为此次悲剧事件\N{\rOriginal text}Press officials say because of the tragedy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:47.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗1号飞行任务将被无限期推迟\N{\rOriginal text}the Apollo 1 flight has now been postponed indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 登月之旅很有吸引力\N{\rOriginal text}I... It's, uh... It's a groovy trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:53.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但在美国 还有很多更重要的事情要先做\N{\rOriginal text}but there are a lot more important things to do first in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也许把这些事情都搞定了 我们才能登月\N{\rOriginal text}Maybe when all that's taken care of we can afford to go to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:59.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们发现自己物质丰富 士气低下\N{\rOriginal text}We find ourselves rich in goods but ragged in spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}雄心勃勃地想要登月\N{\rOriginal text}Reaching with magnificent precision for the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}却在地球上陷入一片混乱\N{\rOriginal text}but falling into raucous discord on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们想要和平 却被卷入战争\N{\rOriginal text}We are caught at war wanting peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们想要团结 却四分五裂\N{\rOriginal text}We're torn by division wanting unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这个巨大的土星号火箭\N{\rOriginal text}This giant Saturn rocket
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:14.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}以及这里的其他设备 最初都是这场竞赛的一部分\N{\rOriginal text}and the rest of the equipment here began as part of a race
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:14.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(国家航空航天局预算削减)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}为的是战胜苏联人 它们肩负着\N{\rOriginal text}to beat the Russians with the national goal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我国在这个十年内把人类送上月球的目标\N{\rOriginal text}of putting a man on the moon in this decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:23.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但登月之旅的花费将超出所有人的预期\N{\rOriginal text}But their trip will cost more than anyone thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:28.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而在1960年代成功登月的几率愈加渺茫\N{\rOriginal text}And their chances of landing on the moon in the 1960s are increasingly slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(国家航空航天局)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:51.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}斯图 你当主管第一周 听着情况不妙啊\N{\rOriginal text}First week as manager, Stu. Doesn't sound like it's going great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}要么是计量表不准 要么是某个储存罐漏了\N{\rOriginal text}So either our meters are off or there's a breach in one of the tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但这种情况没有规程 我们也找不到泄漏源头\N{\rOriginal text}But there's no protocol for this. And we can't source the leak
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为是液态... 液态氢\N{\rOriginal text}because it's liquid hyd... Liquid hydrogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}它是无色无味的 所有人都出去 快\N{\rOriginal text}It's colorless and odorless. Everybody out! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}里德 凯尔 放下铅笔\N{\rOriginal text}Reed, Kyle, pencils down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:05.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可能已经在燃烧了 我们却不知情 找门出去\N{\rOriginal text}It could be burning, and we wouldn't know it. Find a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:08.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}快 跑起来 别慢吞吞的\N{\rOriginal text}Come on! Run, run! No walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他在干什么? 打扫吗?\N{\rOriginal text}What's he doing? Is he cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不... 这是... 一种检查泄漏的老办法\N{\rOriginal text}No, no. It's an... It's an old-school leak detection process.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他用的是把扫帚\N{\rOriginal text}It's a broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}斯图 你很聪明的 再想想 干麦秆加上液态氢等于...\N{\rOriginal text}Stu, you're better than this. Come on. Straw plus liquid hydrogen equals...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 没事了 别担心了 来吧\N{\rOriginal text}All right, we're good! Don't worry about it. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们还有工作呢 快点\N{\rOriginal text}We got work to do. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}新的规程是用扫帚检查泄漏\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, the new protocol is the broom method.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们需要一把新扫帚\N{\rOriginal text}We need a new broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我刚才真以为他死了\N{\rOriginal text}I for sure thought he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜托\N{\rOriginal text}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这还是\N{\rOriginal text}It's still broke
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:11.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你上次发脾气时弄坏的 是的 我能看出来\N{\rOriginal text}from the last time you were in a mood. Yeah, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:14.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}波音又来电话了 亨利 打给议会 别找我\N{\rOriginal text}Boeing called again. Call Congress, Henry, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我没有他们的电话号码\N{\rOriginal text}I don't have their number.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:20.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每天... 这里都有东西坏掉\N{\rOriginal text}Every day, every day, something is breaking around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:24.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}或者爆炸 我们资金不足 人手不足\N{\rOriginal text}Or blowing up. We're underfunded, under... understaffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但没错 他们还期望我们吊打苏联人\N{\rOriginal text}But yeah, we're still expected to beat the pants off the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你能告诉我到底该怎么做到吗?\N{\rOriginal text}You mind telling me how the hell we're supposed to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就从善待自动售货机开始吧\N{\rOriginal text}Could start by being a little nicer to the vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}快看 在那里\N{\rOriginal text}Ooh! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什么? 有一只猫\N{\rOriginal text}What? There's a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那又怎么了? 是一只黑猫 亨利 代表霉运\N{\rOriginal text}So what? It's a black cat, Henry. It's bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 不见了\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:46.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 谢天谢地 好吧 我们走\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Thank God. Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}叫保安 不要\N{\rOriginal text}Call security. I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不叫 这... 你要去叫\N{\rOriginal text}I will not. It... Yes, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:53.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们这里最不该出现的就是一只黑猫\N{\rOriginal text}The last thing that we need around here is a black cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:55.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}保安又不管这种事\N{\rOriginal text}They don't deal with things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们管的 现在管了\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, they do. They do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你反应过头了 不 是你反应迟钝\N{\rOriginal text}Y-You're overreacting. No, you're not overreacting enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}立刻叫保安 马上去\N{\rOriginal text}Call 'em right now. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我看起来如何?\N{\rOriginal text}How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}容光焕发 加油\N{\rOriginal text}You're glowing. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}下午好 小伙子们\N{\rOriginal text}Good afternoon, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}走错房间了 亲爱的 我们不需要笔录\N{\rOriginal text}Wrong room, sweetheart. We don't need dictation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:28.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我叫凯莉·琼斯 今天的会议由我主持\N{\rOriginal text}I'm Kelly Jones. I'll be running the meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:30.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们一定是菲尔·亨利 尼尔·布朗和...\N{\rOriginal text}You must be Phil Hunley, Neil Brown and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:34.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}扎克·坦纳 不介意我坐下吧?\N{\rOriginal text}Ooh. [chuckles] Zack Tanner. You don't mind if I sit down, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:37.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}恕我直言 琼斯太太 我们是一家进步的公司\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, all due respect, Mrs. Jones, we're a progressive company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们的速记员团队有16名女性\N{\rOriginal text}We employ 16 women in our steno pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:44.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们向男人出售跑车 出售300马力...\N{\rOriginal text}We're selling sports cars to men. We're selling a 300 horsepower...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:48.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}355马力 你们卖的是7014CC排量 V8引擎的猛兽\N{\rOriginal text}355, 428 cubic inch V-8 beast is what you're selling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们要着重推销车的速度 比如这个\N{\rOriginal text}You want to focus on the car's speed. Something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:58.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}眼熟吗? 雪佛兰科迈罗 庞蒂亚克火鸟 还有奥斯莫比尔\N{\rOriginal text}Look familiar? Chevy Camaro. Pontiac Firebird. And Oldsmobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}都是上个月的\N{\rOriginal text}All from last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}幸好你们有些竞争对手没有的东西\N{\rOriginal text}Thankfully, you have something that your competition doesn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:09.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}野马Fastback “给他355马力 给家人安全带”\N{\rOriginal text}The Mustang Fastback. "355 horses for him. Seat belts for the family."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:13.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}安全带? 我们安装安全带 只是因为明年可能会有强制安装的规定\N{\rOriginal text}The seat belts? We only put them in because they might be mandatory next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们来做个游戏吧\N{\rOriginal text}Let's play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:18.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我来猜你们几位先生分别驾驶什么车\N{\rOriginal text}Now I'm gonna guess what kind of car each one of you gentlemen drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:28.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}扎克 1966年款福特野马敞篷车 罂粟红色的\N{\rOriginal text}Zack, Ford Mustang '66 convertible. It's poppy red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:35.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不过你们当了老公的人不会开野马 尼尔开林肯大陆\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, no Mustangs for you husbands though. A Lincoln Continental for Neil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:43.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可怜的菲尔开客货两用车 菲尔 你知道我每天什么时候最开心吗?\N{\rOriginal text}A station wagon for poor Phil. Oh, Phil. You know what the best part of my day is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是我老公查理晚上回家时\N{\rOriginal text}When my husband Charlie comes home at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:55.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我无法想象他有一天晚上不回家会怎样\N{\rOriginal text}I can't even imagine what it would be like if-if one night he... he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你来想象一下这段对话\N{\rOriginal text}Now imagine the conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:02.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果有人跟你老婆说这辆车\N{\rOriginal text}if someone told your wife that this car,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:05.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拥有355马力和169公里的最高时速\N{\rOriginal text}its 355 horses and 105 top speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:10.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}正是这辆车每天晚上 载着她老公安全回到家人身边\N{\rOriginal text}this car is what brings her husband home safe to her family every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她希望你拥有这辆车\N{\rOriginal text}Now she wants you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她说出每个已婚男士梦想听到的话\N{\rOriginal text}She says the words every married man dreams of hearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“如果你买下这辆野马\N{\rOriginal text}"I'd feel so much better
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我会感觉比现在更幸福 亲爱的”\N{\rOriginal text}if you bought yourself that Mustang, sweetheart."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎么猜到他们开什么车的?\N{\rOriginal text}How did you guess what kind of cars they drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}贿赂了他们的秘书还是怎样?\N{\rOriginal text}What, bribe their secretaries or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉 真的假的\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}两包维珍妮牌女士香烟和一瓶帕科香水\N{\rOriginal text}Two packs of Virginia Slims and a bottle of Paco Rabanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每个人都是有价的\N{\rOriginal text}Everyone has their price.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:45.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}幸好刚才我的羊水没破 天啊\N{\rOriginal text}I'm just lucky that my water didn't break in there. Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 罗恩 你老婆好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Hi, Ron. How's the wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(创意总监 凯莉·琼斯)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}听着 假肚子只能干洗\N{\rOriginal text}Now, the baby bump, dry-clean only.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好的 我记下了 还有 欧米茄确认了下周的安排\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, I have that noted. A-Also, Omega confirmed for next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我完成了芭斯·罗缤的画\N{\rOriginal text}I finished the Baskin-Robbins artwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}Palmex那个人问你的地址 想给你送玫瑰\N{\rOriginal text}and that guy from Palmex asked for your address to send roses,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我给了他我的 我知道\N{\rOriginal text}but I gave him mine because I know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你对玫瑰的看法 你知道我对玫瑰的看法\N{\rOriginal text}how you feel about roses. You know how I feel about roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:08.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}还有 约翰又来电了 他想在星期二带你去吃晚餐\N{\rOriginal text}Also, John called. Again. He wants to take you to dinner Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}告诉他我搬到洛杉矶去了 给陶氏化学的布鲁斯打电话\N{\rOriginal text}Tell him I moved to LA. And call Bruce from Dow Chemical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:13.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我听说他们在给密保诺密封袋找新代理\N{\rOriginal text}I hear they're looking for a new agency for Ziploc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人们应该抵制陶氏化学 他们做凝固汽油弹\N{\rOriginal text}People should be boycotting Dow. They make napalm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:19.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人们嘴上说着抵制 但还是在买装三文治的袋子\N{\rOriginal text}People say they're boycotting, but they're still buying sandwich bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们还卖保鲜膜和泡沫塑料\N{\rOriginal text}They also sell Saran Wrap and Styrofoam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你认为人们会停止使用泡沫塑料吗? 你的咖啡用什么装的?\N{\rOriginal text}Think people are going to stop using Styrofoam? What's your coffee in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}听着 我知道你和你的朋友们想拯救世界\N{\rOriginal text}Now, I know you and your friends want to save the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但等到你在1984年当上这里的主管\N{\rOriginal text}and by the time you're running this place in 1984,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}世上已经没有核弹 全体人类平权了\N{\rOriginal text}there's gonna be no nukes and equal rights for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但在那之前 我们得干好本职工作\N{\rOriginal text}But until then, we've got a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:39.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉... 我们有大麻烦了\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly! Kelly! Kelly. Kelly. We've got a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:43.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我刚刚愤怒地离开片场 对 我有充分的理由\N{\rOriginal text}I just stormed off set, and, yes, it was justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我没法跟胡佛这些人合作\N{\rOriginal text}I cannot work with these Hoover people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:50.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}显然他们对我给他们拍广告的方式有意见\N{\rOriginal text}Apparently, they have issues with the way that I am shooting their commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们真是这么说的 “他们的” 那可是我的广告\N{\rOriginal text}They actually said that. "Their." It's my commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不就是做吸尘器的嘛 我可是搞艺术的\N{\rOriginal text}They make vacuums. I make art.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉 我们约了见面吗? 没有...\N{\rOriginal text}Sorry, did we have a meeting set? No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不好意思 我没意识到还得约时间\N{\rOriginal text}I'm sorry. I didn't realize I had to set a time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}才能跟最亲爱的朋友说话\N{\rOriginal text}to speak to one of my dearest friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}上次我们说话时你把我炒了 我现在不为你工作了\N{\rOriginal text}The last time we spoke, you fired me. And I don't work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我跟你讲 凯莉 我不是来听你训斥的\N{\rOriginal text}You know what, Kelly, I didn't come in here to be berated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是来找你支持我的\N{\rOriginal text}I came in to be agreed with!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:09.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你十分钟后要向雀巢推销 这很重要\N{\rOriginal text}You have that Nestlé pitch in ten. Very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}骗人的 再见\N{\rOriginal text}That is a lie. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:15.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}兰斯 给你拿到这份导演工作 堪称圣诞奇迹\N{\rOriginal text}Lance, getting you this directing gig was a Christmas miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你搞砸了那个果冻广告拍摄后 我用了三周时间\N{\rOriginal text}It took me three weeks to convince them that you were stable
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}才说服他们你并非喜怒无常 果冻广告那事不怪我\N{\rOriginal text}after your Jell-O shoot from hell. Jell-O was not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:24.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那个演员... 才五岁 你把他弄哭了\N{\rOriginal text}Ugh. That actor wa... Was five. You made him cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是帮了那孩子一把 好莱坞可不好混\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I did that child a favor. Hollywood is no cakewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:30.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那亨氏食品广告呢? 你超了预算四万块 只是个番茄酱广告而已\N{\rOriginal text}What about the Heinz commercial? You went 40,000 over budget. It was about ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:34.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}才不是 重点是番茄酱带来的希望\N{\rOriginal text}It was not about ketchup. It was about the promise of ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没有人看到我在为他们的产品做什么\N{\rOriginal text}No one sees what I'm doing for their products.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我在提升产品价值\N{\rOriginal text}I am elevating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:40.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我现在应该在拍电影了\N{\rOriginal text}I should be in film by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我拒绝了执导《娃娃谷》的机会\N{\rOriginal text}I passed on directing Valley of the Dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:46.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那事怪我 但我还是该拍电影 好了 我们是怎么称呼你的?\N{\rOriginal text}That is on me, but still. Now, what do we call you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}广告界的库布里克 好了 天啊 斯坦利是半吊子\N{\rOriginal text}The Kubrick of commercials. All right. Oh, my God. Stanley is a hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拍出一部好电影就突然成了天才\N{\rOriginal text}He does one good movie, and suddenly he's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:54.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你是传奇 好吗? 创意天才\N{\rOriginal text}You are a legend, right? Creative genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:57.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但你也脾气暴躁 反复无常 永远不能按预算拍摄\N{\rOriginal text}You're also hotheaded, mercurial and can't stick to a budget for shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}谢谢 这不是夸你\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, thank you. That wasn't a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:02.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这时就该当耳旁风 你若不跟胡佛合作 以后就没人请你了\N{\rOriginal text}It is when you stop listening. If you quit Hoover, you'll be unhirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}兰斯 不如你回片场吧\N{\rOriginal text}Lance, why don't you march your ass back to set,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不管发什么脾气 都道个歉 好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}and you apologize for whatever fit you threw, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}给你男朋友买个棒棒的圣诞礼物 谢谢他容忍你\N{\rOriginal text}Buy your boyfriend something nice for Christmas for putting up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也给我买个礼物 好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Get something for me too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:17.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}圣诞快乐 兰斯 圣诞快乐\N{\rOriginal text}Merry Christmas, Lance. Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请你给我找份像样的工作 好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Can you get me a decent job, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗8号于今早成功发射\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 8 launched successfully this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:32.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这场胜利是国家航空航天局的及时雨 在越南方面 今天有更多人牺牲\N{\rOriginal text}A much needed win for NASA. In Vietnam, more men were lost today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:32.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(阿波罗8号发射录影)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}二千五百万公里...\N{\rOriginal text}And 15 million miles...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}麻烦再来一杯 另外把晚餐菜单拿给我\N{\rOriginal text}I'll have another round, please, and a look at the dinner menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好的 女士 谢谢\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, ma'am. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:44.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}今晚有两个特色菜 鸡肉馅饼和洛克菲勒牡蛎\N{\rOriginal text}Two specials tonight. Chicken potpie and Oysters Rockefeller.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们吃鸡好了 她对牡蛎过敏\N{\rOriginal text}We'll do the chicken. She's allergic to oysters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:53.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}给我来一杯麦卡伦 一个柠檬和一个砧板\N{\rOriginal text}And I'll take a shot of Macallan, a lemon and a cutting board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好的 先生 不好意思 我认识你吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, sir. Oh, I'm sorry. Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:01.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跑车上装安全带 这个点子很不错\N{\rOriginal text}Seat belts in a sports car. I mean, that's a great angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:04.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很不幸 他们即将停止跟你合作\N{\rOriginal text}Unfortunately, they're about to kill the account.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}为什么?\N{\rOriginal text}Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:11.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为有人告诉他们 你肚子里其实没孩子\N{\rOriginal text}Because someone told them that you don't really have a bun in the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}菲尔 让我解释一下\N{\rOriginal text}Phil. [chuckles] Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我以后再也不会相信女人了\N{\rOriginal text}That's the last time I trust a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我还给你送了一份婴儿礼物\N{\rOriginal text}I actually sent you a baby gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你那么做非常贴心 请让我...\N{\rOriginal text}Which was so sweet, by the way. Let me just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼尔 让我解释一下 如果你们...\N{\rOriginal text}Neil, let-let me explain. If you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎么回事? 你为谁工作? 奥美广告?\N{\rOriginal text}What is this? Who do you work for, Ogilvy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你业绩拼不过我 就害我被解雇?\N{\rOriginal text}Huh? You can't outsell me, so you got me fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:34.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}恰恰相反 我想聘请你\N{\rOriginal text}Just the opposite. I wanna hire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:39.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我叫莫·伯克斯 在总统办公室工作\N{\rOriginal text}Name's Moe Berkus. I work for the president's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哪家公司的?\N{\rOriginal text}Of what company?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}美国总统\N{\rOriginal text}The president.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:54.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们需要一位营销专家 听说你是最厉害的\N{\rOriginal text}We need a, uh, marketing specialist, and word has it you are the very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:13:00.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}于是我做了些调研 发现...\N{\rOriginal text}So I did a little digging, and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你的经历很有趣 凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}You have quite a colorful past, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:06.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}还是说我该叫你简? 来自芝加哥的空姐\N{\rOriginal text}Or should I call you Jane? Stewardess from Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:11.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也许你更喜欢被称为艾米 俄亥俄州的护士\N{\rOriginal text}Or perhaps you would prefer Amy, the nurse from Ohio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:14.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有这么漂亮的脸蛋 谁还会看推荐信?\N{\rOriginal text}Face like that, who's gonna check references?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你找的那一页不在这里\N{\rOriginal text}Page you're looking for isn't in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不知道你在说什么\N{\rOriginal text}I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你当然不知道 我懂\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, sure you don't. And I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:32.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 我也有几十个身份证 我的真名也不叫莫\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, I have dozens of IDs, and my real name's not Moe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有那么多名字可以选 你却挑了“莫”?\N{\rOriginal text}With all the names you could've picked, you landed on Moe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你天赋出众\N{\rOriginal text}You have singular talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:41.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可以用来成就更伟大的事业 何必浪费在卖车上呢?\N{\rOriginal text}Why waste it selling cars when you can think bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:46.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫 有什么公司比福特更伟大?\N{\rOriginal text}Well, Moe, what's bigger than Ford?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你去过佛罗里达州吗?\N{\rOriginal text}You ever been to Florida?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们想让你推销月球? 月球 阿波罗任务\N{\rOriginal text}They want you to sell the moon? The moon. The Apollo mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一整套\N{\rOriginal text}The whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这个叫莫的家伙为国家航空航天局做事?\N{\rOriginal text}And this Moe guy works for NASA?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:08.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 不 算是吧 他是政府的人\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. I mean, y... Well, no. Um, kind of. He-He-He works for the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哪个部门?\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, which part?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:19.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这个人... 我们在为理查德·尼克松工作?\N{\rOriginal text}Does this guy... Are we working for Richard Nixon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为我才不会为理查德·尼克松工作 凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}Because, Kelly, I will not work for Richard Nixon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是持证女权主义者 我真的有证\N{\rOriginal text}I'm a card-carrying feminist. I actually have a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我甚至不相信他要当总统了\N{\rOriginal text}I can't even believe he's going to be president.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:29.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我本来不知道自己对美国有这么多意见\N{\rOriginal text}I had no idea I disagreed with this much of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:33.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们为国家航空航天局工作 推销月球 没人对月球有意见\N{\rOriginal text}We are working for NASA to sell the moon. Nobody disagrees about the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不是 你我都清楚\N{\rOriginal text}No. You and I both know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们身边每天都有可怕的事发生\N{\rOriginal text}that everywhere around us every day something terrible is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}无所不在\N{\rOriginal text}Everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:41.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}除了太空\N{\rOriginal text}Except in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真讨厌 你说动我了 他们绝对需要我们的帮助\N{\rOriginal text}I hate that this is working on me. They definitely need our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:48.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你知道国家航空航天局的头29次任务 只有48%的成功率吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Did you know of NASA's first 29 missions, only 48% have been successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:50.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这不可能 太离谱了\N{\rOriginal text}That can't be. That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:56.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你知道可可海滩市的 男女比例是五比一吗? 天啊\N{\rOriginal text}Did you know the ratio of men to women in Cocoa Beach is 5-to-1? [chuckles] Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}只要你给我们找的住处不在兄弟会街就行\N{\rOriginal text}As long as you got us a quiet place that's not on Frat Row.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}指南手册说那里很古雅\N{\rOriginal text}The... The guidebook said it's quaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(卫星汽车旅馆 客满)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你被炒鱿鱼了\N{\rOriginal text}You're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这些都是什么人啊?\N{\rOriginal text}Who are all these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:23.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}今天星期三 他们好像在另一个星球上\N{\rOriginal text}It is a Wednesday. It's like they're on a different planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这里叫佛罗里达\N{\rOriginal text}They call it Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请告诉我你订了一个远离游泳池的房间\N{\rOriginal text}Please tell me you booked a room away from the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}16 21 天气\N{\rOriginal text}sixteen and 21... Weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}明天晴间多云\N{\rOriginal text}Clear to partly cloudy tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}下午及傍晚 局部地区有雷阵雨\N{\rOriginal text}A few isolated thundershowers during the afternoon and early evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(佛罗里达州 可可海滩)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}今晚最低气温18至24摄氏度\N{\rOriginal text}A low tonight, 65 to 75.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}目前月球火箭发射场周边城市 气温25摄氏度\N{\rOriginal text}Currently 77 in the Moonport cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:51.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这里是KO2020电台 为你带来的体育新闻和天气预报\N{\rOriginal text}That's KO twenty-twenty news, sports and weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}WKKO\N{\rOriginal text}WKKO...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:55.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(沃尔菲餐厅)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 乔 晚上好 科尔 来点什么?\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, Joe. Evening, Cole. What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}黑咖啡\N{\rOriginal text}Coffee. Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:09.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}再来点最快能打包带走的吃的 朋友\N{\rOriginal text}And whatever takes the least amount of time to put in a bag, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}小姐 你很惹火\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, miss, you're on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真有创意\N{\rOriginal text}Very original.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}得了 我不想跟你玩干柴烈火\N{\rOriginal text}No, I do not wanna stop, drop and roll with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不是 你的书着火了\N{\rOriginal text}No, your book is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:51.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊\N{\rOriginal text}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:58.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 没事的... 我的天\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. All right. All right. All right. Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉 谢谢你 我只是... 教你个经验法则\N{\rOriginal text}I'm sorry. Thank you. I just... Just as a rule of thumb,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}酒精和火焰 绝配\N{\rOriginal text}alcohol and flames, they... they like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:06.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 天啊 我把你的外套烧坏了\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Oh, gosh. I-I-I ruined your jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没事 这衣服跟我出生入死\N{\rOriginal text}No, this thing's seen worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}经历过千锤百炼 请你喝一杯补偿你吧\N{\rOriginal text}Been through worse. Let me buy a drink for your troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不必了 必须的\N{\rOriginal text}That's not necessary. I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不喝酒 没关系\N{\rOriginal text}I don't drink. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:15.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真的? 不喝酒的宇航员 真有意思\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, really? An astronaut who doesn't drink. That's very intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎么会认为我是宇航员?\N{\rOriginal text}What makes you think I'm an astronaut?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:21.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为你戴着阿波罗胸针 只有宇航员才有\N{\rOriginal text}Because you have an Apollo pin, and only astronauts get those.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}看来你对国家航空航天局略知一二\N{\rOriginal text}So you know a thing or two about NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:27.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 我是新晋粉丝 我叫凯莉·琼斯\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, well, I'm a recent fan. I'm Kelly Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:31.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不是宇航员 我只是在肯尼迪中心工作 科尔·戴维斯\N{\rOriginal text}I'm no astronaut. I just work at Kennedy. Cole Davis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你做什么工作?\N{\rOriginal text}Well, what do you do there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:39.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}听着 我最不愿意在闲聊中谈工作\N{\rOriginal text}Uh... Look, the last thing I want to do is make small talk about my job. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉 我不是那个意思\N{\rOriginal text}Sorry. That didn't sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不是想... 没关系 对 你只是实话实说\N{\rOriginal text}I didn't mean it for it to... Uh. That's okay. No. You were being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你点的餐好了 科尔\N{\rOriginal text}Order up, Cole. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:14.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我没实话实说 如果我真的坦诚\N{\rOriginal text}I wasn't being honest. If I was being honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我会跟你说 你是我记忆中\N{\rOriginal text}I'd have told you you're the most beautiful woman
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:18.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所见过最美的女人\N{\rOriginal text}that I've seen in longer than I can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而我的记忆力很好\N{\rOriginal text}and I have a very good memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只想请你喝一杯 然后跟你聊上几小时\N{\rOriginal text}All I really want to do is just buy you a drink and talk to you for hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我做不到 所以我要努力忘记你在这里\N{\rOriginal text}but I can't so I'm trying really hard to just forget that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很高兴认识你 凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}It was nice to meet you, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常抱歉\N{\rOriginal text}I really am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}欢迎来到火箭路\N{\rOriginal text}Welcome to Rockets Road,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:30.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}又称鳄鱼巷\N{\rOriginal text}also known as Alligator Alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:34.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果想保住胳膊和腿\N{\rOriginal text}You'll wanna keep your arms and legs inside the cart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请不要把手脚伸出车外\N{\rOriginal text}if you wanna keep your arms and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:42.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没有啦 开个小玩笑 它们主要在水中发动攻击\N{\rOriginal text}No, that's just a little joke. They mostly attack in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:42.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(国家航空航天局 约翰F 肯尼迪航天中心)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:46.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 今天的参观大约要两个半到三小时\N{\rOriginal text}Now, today's tour will take approximately two and a half to three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请舒适地坐好\N{\rOriginal text}So let's get comfy-cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}右手边是我们的测试楼\N{\rOriginal text}Now on the right is our testing facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是世界顶尖水平的\N{\rOriginal text}State-of-the-art.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}失火了 它经常失火\N{\rOriginal text}It's on fire. It is often on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:01.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}前方是载具组装大楼\N{\rOriginal text}Up ahead, we have the vehicle assembly building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:04.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是组装火箭的地方\N{\rOriginal text}That's where they assemble the rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:10.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是全世界最高的单层建筑\N{\rOriginal text}That is the tallest single-story building in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}里面能放下四座自由女神像\N{\rOriginal text}You can fit four Statue of Liberties inside that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 《生活》杂志 完全没拍出它有多壮观\N{\rOriginal text}Wow. Life Magazine really doesn't do it justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这也太... 我想进去看看\N{\rOriginal text}This is so gre... I'd love to go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:21.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这里严禁入内 抱歉 走 我们靠近点看看\N{\rOriginal text}It's highly restricted. I'm sorry. Come on, let's get a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不行... 这里不得进入\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, no, no. No. There's no entry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你需要一个特殊的胸卡才能进\N{\rOriginal text}You need a special access badge to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}比如这个? 对\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, like... like this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:32.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那... 不行... 那是我的胸卡\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. That's, uh... Oh, no, no, no, that's... that's my badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 看看这地方 太大了\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, hey... Oh. Look at this place. It's enormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}似乎大得多... 她们拿走了我的胸卡\N{\rOriginal text}It seems like it's much bigger... They took my badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}看看这个建筑\N{\rOriginal text}I mean, look at this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}喂 那是我的胸卡 你好 先生 嗨\N{\rOriginal text}Hello? That's-That's my badge. Hello, sir. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是国家航空航天局 公共事务部的凯莉·琼斯\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly Jones from NASA Public Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:45.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是我们俩的万能通行证 谢谢\N{\rOriginal text}Here's our all-access pass for both of us. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}谢谢 等等... 我的胸卡\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you. Wait, wait. My card.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:54.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这个我能推销出去\N{\rOriginal text}Now, this I can sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:01.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哟呼\N{\rOriginal text}Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:05.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们好 小伙子们...\N{\rOriginal text}Hello. Boys, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 凯莉·琼斯\N{\rOriginal text}Hi. Kelly Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:09.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是国家航空航天局 新成立的公共事务部的\N{\rOriginal text}I'm from the new NASA Public Affairs team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我能问你们俩几个问题吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Can I ask you two a few questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}姓名 年龄 你们在这里的工作?\N{\rOriginal text}Name, age, and what's your job here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:19.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是斯图·布莱斯 总工程师之一 24岁\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, I'm Stu Bryce. One of the, uh, head engineers, and I'm 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们就说35岁 好\N{\rOriginal text}We'll say 35. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:21.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你呢?\N{\rOriginal text}And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:24.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我叫唐·哈珀 我是他的手下 23岁\N{\rOriginal text}I'm Don Harper. I-I work for him, and I'm 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们真年轻\N{\rOriginal text}You guys are babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:29.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}国家航空航天局的平均年龄是26岁\N{\rOriginal text}The average age at NASA is 26.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我们知道这里也有些老年人\N{\rOriginal text}But w-we do know some old people that work here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 32 33岁的 是\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, like, 32, 33. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}听你们这么说 我很想杀了你俩\N{\rOriginal text}I'll try not to kill both of you for saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:39.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跟我们说说 斯图 你为什么加入这伟大的美国任务?\N{\rOriginal text}So, tell us, Stu, what brings you to join this great American mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:42.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我在大学宿舍里看到了一张传单\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I s... saw a, uh, flyer in my college dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“从小就热爱群星” 很好\N{\rOriginal text}"A childhood love of the stars." That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常感人 非常好\N{\rOriginal text}That's very moving. That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你呢? 不好意思\N{\rOriginal text}And you? Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎么来了?\N{\rOriginal text}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:56.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我特意来找你的 想给你我的电话号码\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I... I tracked you down to give you my phone number,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为我感觉我们很来电\N{\rOriginal text}'cause I felt we had a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:01.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什么? 别紧张 我开玩笑的\N{\rOriginal text}What? Relax. I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:04.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我现在在这里工作 莫·伯克斯招我进来 改组国家航空航天局公共事务部\N{\rOriginal text}I work here now. Moe Berkus brought me on to revamp NASA Public Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:07.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你就是来自曼哈顿的广告精英\N{\rOriginal text}So you're the killer from Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你一定就是发射主管 这是我的同事露比·马丁\N{\rOriginal text}And you must be the launch director. This is my associate, Ruby Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:14.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我不在乎 听着 这栋楼完全禁止进入\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, I don't care. Look. This building is completely off-limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这里有各种可能烧伤 冻伤 烤焦\N{\rOriginal text}Everything in here can burn you, freeze you, fry you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:18.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}毒死 砸死你们的东西\N{\rOriginal text}poison you and crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:20.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}走吧 出去 你在这里工作多久了?\N{\rOriginal text}So let's go. Out. How long have you worked here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:23.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很长时间了\N{\rOriginal text}A substantial amount of time. Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:25.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你在写什么? 你的原话\N{\rOriginal text}What are you writing? Your quote.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:27.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这不算原话 我只是随口一说\N{\rOriginal text}That's not a quote. It was just a thing that I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我会添油加醋的 你今天有时间接受采访吗?\N{\rOriginal text}I'll punch it up. Do you have time today for an interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:32.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我还需要跟你的上级谈谈\N{\rOriginal text}And also, I need to sit down with your senior officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}上相的优先 我可以帮忙挑\N{\rOriginal text}The photogenic types first. I can help with the selection process.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:36.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}听着 我这里的人都太奇怪了 不适合采访\N{\rOriginal text}Look, my guys are too weird for interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:38.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而且他们真的在忙生死攸关的工作\N{\rOriginal text}and they're actually busy doing life-and-death work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:42.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 我不需要你的批准\N{\rOriginal text}Well, you know, I don't need your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:45.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}美国人跟太空之间 漫长且昂贵的蜜月期已经结束\N{\rOriginal text}The Americans are over their long and expensive honeymoon in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是来提醒大家当初为什么爱上太空的\N{\rOriginal text}and I'm here to remind them why they fell in love in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:51.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是吗? 美国人应该心存感激\N{\rOriginal text}Is that right? Well, Americans should be very grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:54.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这些人为了这项任务在冒生命危险\N{\rOriginal text}that these men are putting their lives on the line for the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:58.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你并不怎么了解美国人 是吧?\N{\rOriginal text}Well, you don't know much about American people, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:02.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你也不怎么了解 你的办公室吧? 我带你看看\N{\rOriginal text}You don't know very much about your office I'm about to show you, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:11.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是储物间吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Is this a storage closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:13.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不是 储物间有窗户\N{\rOriginal text}Nope. Storage closet has a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:16.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 速溶咖啡在休息室\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, so, instant coffee... is in the break room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}记得先把水龙头打开 放一分钟的水 把铁锈冲掉\N{\rOriginal text}Just run the tap for a minute to flush out the rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:23.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们有谁会用灭火器吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Do either of you know how to work a fire extinguisher?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:27.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不会? 好吧 四步口诀 很简单\N{\rOriginal text}No? Mkay. PASS method's pretty simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拔安全销 对准火焰 压下把手 喷向火焰\N{\rOriginal text}Just, uh, pull the pin, aim, squeeze, sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:33.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果你们有任何其他需要\N{\rOriginal text}If you need anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:36.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可以回纽约去拿 祝你们愉快\N{\rOriginal text}uh, maybe just go back to New York and get it. Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:41.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}至少他还算养眼 但说话很刺耳\N{\rOriginal text}Well, at least he's easy on the eyes. He's hard on the ears though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:44.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}欢迎仪式很烂啊 我以为你说他们想要我们帮忙呢\N{\rOriginal text}Not a great welcome wagon. I thought you said they wanted our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:47.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 我说他们需要我们帮忙 这一点现在已经实锤到不能再实锤\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, no. I said they needed our help. And I do believe that now more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:50.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果我们谁都不能谈或什么都不能看\N{\rOriginal text}How are we supposed to do that if we can't talk to anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:52.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那要怎么帮忙?\N{\rOriginal text}or look at anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:55.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是一只猫...\N{\rOriginal text}Aw, it's a cat. It's a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.49,0:23:56.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是一只猫 是一只猫\N{\rOriginal text}It's a cat! It's a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:58.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你知道关于黑猫的说法吗?\N{\rOriginal text}You know what they say about black cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:01.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果黑猫从你面前路过 可能是要去其他地方\N{\rOriginal text}If they cross your path, they're probably going someplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.54,0:24:05.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 该把旧名片夹翻出来了\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, time to dig out the old Rolodex.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.04,0:24:08.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}创意时间到\N{\rOriginal text}Let's get creative.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.61,0:24:34.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗11号将把我们的人送上月球\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 11 will land our men on the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.49,0:24:37.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这会让我们成为世界第一\N{\rOriginal text}and that makes us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:40.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果我们完成工作 将会在那里发射\N{\rOriginal text}If we do our jobs, we will launch right from there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.75,0:24:43.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}时间是7月16日一大早\N{\rOriginal text}July 16, bright and early.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:44.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在那之前\N{\rOriginal text}Between now and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.62,0:24:47.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们要完成人类历史上\N{\rOriginal text}we will piece together the biggest jigsaw puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.50,0:24:49.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}最大的拼图\N{\rOriginal text}in the history of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.38,0:24:52.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}六百万个零部件散落在全国各地\N{\rOriginal text}Six million parts spread out around the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:55.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们要对每一个零件 进行组装 测试 再测试\N{\rOriginal text}and we will assemble, test, and retest every single one
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.68,0:24:58.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}直到我们确定阿波罗11号 可以万无一失地发射\N{\rOriginal text}until we are certain that Apollo 11 will take off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.22,0:25:01.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}并飞向月球 就在...\N{\rOriginal text}without a hitch and head to the moon in...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.77,0:25:02.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}亨利 你说\N{\rOriginal text}Henry, sing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.56,0:25:05.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在七个月后\N{\rOriginal text}Seven months. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.65,0:25:06.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}七个月后\N{\rOriginal text}Seven months.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.94,0:25:10.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请帮我恭喜阿波罗11号的宇航员\N{\rOriginal text}Please help me congratulate the astronauts of Apollo 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.07,0:25:14.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿姆斯特朗 奥尔德林和柯林斯\N{\rOriginal text}Armstrong, Aldrin and Collins.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.46,0:25:29.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿... 伙计们 你们觉得白宫怎么样?\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, hey! How'd you like the White House, boys? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.88,0:25:28.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(月球 我们来了)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.34,0:25:32.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}还不错 只可惜尼尔不让我偷那里的瓷器\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, it was all right, except Neil wouldn't let me steal the china.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.55,0:25:39.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 因为在八个月后 等这一切都结束\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Because in eight months, when this is all over,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.22,0:25:43.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们需要新历史书 来记载我们在这里取得的成就时\N{\rOriginal text}and they need new history books to cover what we've accomplished here,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.22,0:25:46.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们每一个人都能说\N{\rOriginal text}each and every single one of you will be able to say that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.19,0:25:51.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“我做了有史以来最困难的事” 对吗?\N{\rOriginal text}"I did the hardest thing that has ever been done." Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.11,0:25:52.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.15,0:25:54.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}行动起来 开工\N{\rOriginal text}Let's do it. Let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.70,0:26:01.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}漂亮 说得好 谢谢\N{\rOriginal text}Beautiful. Perfect. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.87,0:26:03.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 长官\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.79,0:26:07.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你说新来的女士 只要做任何你不喜欢的事就通知你\N{\rOriginal text}you said to tell you when the new lady did anything you wouldn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:09.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我身处肯尼迪航天中心\N{\rOriginal text}I'm here at the Kennedy Space Center
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.79,0:26:12.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有幸采访到副发射主管亨利·斯莫尔斯\N{\rOriginal text}with Deputy Launch Director, Henry Smalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.00,0:26:14.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎么回事? 那是我的名字 他盗用了我的名字和职位\N{\rOriginal text}What's going on? That's my name. He's got my name and my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.92,0:26:18.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这段时间对我们所有人来说都很美好 对我来说更具个人感情\N{\rOriginal text}It's been a great time for all of us. You know, for me, this is very personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.09,0:26:19.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我父亲是一位空军士兵\N{\rOriginal text}My father was an airman...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.43,0:26:20.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是谁啊?\N{\rOriginal text}Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.30,0:26:22.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}反正不是我 他在服役时牺牲了\N{\rOriginal text}It's not me. he died in the line of duty
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.89,0:26:24.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}当时我还是个孩子 我没那么帅\N{\rOriginal text}when I was a child... I'm not that handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.85,0:26:26.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是为了你 老爸\N{\rOriginal text}... so this is for you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.02,0:26:27.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真是够了 听到这个我很遗憾\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, that's it. So sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.89,0:26:30.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}谢谢你的分享 这一定很... 我爸还活着呢\N{\rOriginal text}Thanks for sharing. That must've been... My dad's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.65,0:26:36.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 要怎样才能约在晚上6点左右呢? 好\N{\rOriginal text}Right. What is it that we can do to sort of make 6:00 p.m.? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.57,0:26:39.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}国家航空航天局公共事务部 我是凯莉·琼斯\N{\rOriginal text}NASA Public Affairs, this is Kelly Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.70,0:26:42.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉 美国广播公司 想要下周的媒体录影带\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly, ABC wants next week's press reel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.16,0:26:44.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}还想要我们手上最好的阿波罗8号照片\N{\rOriginal text}They also want the best photo we have from the Apollo 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.41,0:26:46.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跟他们说 如果让我们 上晚6点时间段就给他们\N{\rOriginal text}Tell them they can have it if they give us their 6:00 p.m. time slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.91,0:26:49.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}明白 如果你们播放动画片段\N{\rOriginal text}Got it. If you air an animated segment,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.46,0:26:51.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我能给你们提供独家的... 非常感谢\N{\rOriginal text}I can offer you an exclusive... Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.75,0:26:54.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你父亲是个英雄 你是个英雄 我们非常感激你勤恳地...\N{\rOriginal text}Your father was a hero. You are a hero. We so appreciate you working at...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.55,0:26:57.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是全国广播公司新闻主管 是 我不管 这人是谁?\N{\rOriginal text}That was the head of NBC News. Yeah, I don't care. Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.42,0:26:59.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}谢谢 我们月球上见\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you. See you on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.05,0:27:01.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在公众眼里 他是亨利·斯莫尔斯\N{\rOriginal text}To the world, that's Henry Smalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.59,0:27:02.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他不是亨利·斯莫尔斯\N{\rOriginal text}That's not Henry Smalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.80,0:27:04.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 但你跟我说你们不接受采访\N{\rOriginal text}No, but you told me that your guys don't do interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.85,0:27:06.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所以我只能另请新人\N{\rOriginal text}so I had to hire new guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.60,0:27:11.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你让两位全球最顶尖的工程师装窗户\N{\rOriginal text}You have two of the best engineers on the planet installing a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.81,0:27:14.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}菲尔 你再挥一下锤子 我一定会疯掉\N{\rOriginal text}Phil, if you hammer one more time, I swear to God I'm gonna lose my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.48,0:27:16.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}把锤子放下 摘掉该死的工具带\N{\rOriginal text}Put down the hammer, take your stupid belts off
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.44,0:27:17.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}回去测试\N{\rOriginal text}and get back to testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.49,0:27:20.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}动起来 走了\N{\rOriginal text}On the move. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.70,0:27:22.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这景色绝了吧?\N{\rOriginal text}Can you believe that view?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.28,0:27:24.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们拿到了阿波罗8号的第一批照片 比我的好\N{\rOriginal text}We got the first photos from Apollo 8. It's better than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.66,0:27:26.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}从月球拍的第一张地球照片\N{\rOriginal text}The first shot of the earth from the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.58,0:27:29.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是不是你见过最美的东西?\N{\rOriginal text}Isn't that the most beautiful thing you've ever seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.00,0:27:32.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎么比我先拿到? 他们称之为“地出”\N{\rOriginal text}How'd you get this before me? They're calling it "Earthrise."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.13,0:27:34.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这张照片会登上今晚所有新闻的头条\N{\rOriginal text}It's going to be at the top of every news segment tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.25,0:27:36.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}1968年太糟糕了\N{\rOriginal text}I mean, '68 has been such a terrible year.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.00,0:27:39.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}刺杀 可憎的战争 我们见证了人类最丑恶的一面\N{\rOriginal text}Assassinations, this heinous war, we've seen the worst of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.17,0:27:42.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这时国家航空航天局公布这张照片 一个看世界的全新视角\N{\rOriginal text}Now NASA gives us this? A whole new way to see the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.47,0:27:46.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我会确保所有人都看到\N{\rOriginal text}And I'm gonna make sure everybody sees it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.23,0:27:51.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不能找人冒充别人啊\N{\rOriginal text}You can't just fake people!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.23,0:27:54.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 我是来参加选角的\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, I'm here for the casting. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.23,0:27:58.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他是谁? 是你 你这个角色可抢手了\N{\rOriginal text}Who's he? You. You're a juicy part.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.40,0:28:01.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}要拍这几场戏 这里是角色生平\N{\rOriginal text}So, here's the scenes and the character bio.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.28,0:28:03.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你要扮演的就是这位 所以最好提升一点魅力\N{\rOriginal text}This is the man that you're playing, so you wanna up the charisma a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.78,0:28:05.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我会提升... 明白? 好\N{\rOriginal text}Can do. I'll up the... Okay? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.16,0:28:07.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在朝鲜执行过60次任务? 是的\N{\rOriginal text}Sixty missions in Korea? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.54,0:28:10.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我很荣幸 我在朝鲜飞过52次任务\N{\rOriginal text}It's an honor. I flew 52 missions in Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.79,0:28:11.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我取了个整数\N{\rOriginal text}I rounded up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.25,0:28:17.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“我在朝鲜飞过52次任务” 怎么样?\N{\rOriginal text}"I flew 52 missions in Korea." How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.42,0:28:19.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什么? 我会练习一下的\N{\rOriginal text}What? I'll work on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.84,0:28:25.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她现在都找好人冒充我了\N{\rOriginal text}She has a fake me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.26,0:28:28.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她已经有了个假的我 她有个假的我 假的你\N{\rOriginal text}She got a fake me. She got a fake me and a fake you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.10,0:28:29.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不能冒充你和我 一无所获\N{\rOriginal text}You can't fake me and you. There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.72,0:28:32.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没有莫·伯克斯 我每个字都看过了\N{\rOriginal text}There's no Moe Berkus. I checked every spelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.39,0:28:35.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有个叫莫·伯克斯的打来电话\N{\rOriginal text}I have a Moe Berkus on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.57,0:28:41.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}要我来说吗? 不... 我会很享受的\N{\rOriginal text}Do you want me to talk? Oh, no, no. I'm gonna enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.24,0:28:43.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这将是国家航空航天局史上最快速的解雇\N{\rOriginal text}This is gonna be the fastest firing in NASA's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.91,0:28:47.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 莫 科尔 我听说你在找我\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, Moe. Cole, I hear you're looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.28,0:28:50.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的 凯莉·琼斯 聘请了演员来假扮国家航空航天局工程师\N{\rOriginal text}I am. Kelly Jones hired actors to play NASA engineers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.70,0:28:54.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是不可接受的 我要她今天就走人\N{\rOriginal text}It is unacceptable. I want her desk cleared today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.12,0:28:57.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}冷静点... 好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Calm, calm, calm down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.84,0:29:01.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}华盛顿的政要们会看电视 阿波罗现在上电视了\N{\rOriginal text}Washington watches TV. Apollo is now on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.88,0:29:03.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每个频道 每天都播\N{\rOriginal text}Every channel, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.68,0:29:07.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们想登月吗?\N{\rOriginal text}So, you want to get to the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.26,0:29:09.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我建议你们专心做好本职工作\N{\rOriginal text}I suggest, focus on your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.56,0:29:10.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也让凯莉做好本职工作\N{\rOriginal text}Let Kelly do hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.43,0:29:14.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果她把你打造成舞会上的焦点\N{\rOriginal text}If she's made you the belle of the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.02,0:29:18.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不妨穿上芭蕾舞裙来跳一段\N{\rOriginal text}why don't you just slip on your tutu and do some dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.82,0:29:27.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}炒掉她了?\N{\rOriginal text}She fired? Mm-mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.28,0:29:31.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们被炒了?\N{\rOriginal text}Are we fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.04,0:29:38.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗8号载着宇航员 博尔曼 洛弗尔和安德斯\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 8, carrying astronauts Borman, Lovell and Anders
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.38,0:29:40.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}由土星5号送入了太空\N{\rOriginal text}was launched into space by a Saturn V.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.71,0:29:44.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每一个电视网都在播放地出照片\N{\rOriginal text}Every single network is airing the Earthrise shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.59,0:29:46.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}会传遍世界各地\N{\rOriginal text}I mean, it's... it's gonna be everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.72,0:29:49.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我试着画了几笔\N{\rOriginal text}You know, I tried a little something on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.47,0:29:52.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但好像效果还不行 不够吸引人 我们需要一个关联\N{\rOriginal text}but I just don't think it's working yet. It's not enough. We need a hook,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.39,0:29:55.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一个把登月和人们日常生活挂钩的方法\N{\rOriginal text}a way to weave the moon landing into people's everyday lives
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.06,0:29:56.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}还得潜移默化\N{\rOriginal text}without them realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.19,0:29:59.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 你们有类似沙拉的东西吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, hi. Do you have anything close to a salad?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.23,0:30:01.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}汉堡上的腌黄瓜\N{\rOriginal text}Pickles come on a burger.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.27,0:30:04.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不过要等一等 阿波罗的新闻一出 生意变好了\N{\rOriginal text}It's gonna be a minute, though. Apollo news has business picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.86,0:30:07.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有很多游客想来亲眼见证历史\N{\rOriginal text}All the tourists love to come in and see little pieces of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.36,0:30:11.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}见证历史? 对 比如那支笔\N{\rOriginal text}Pieces of history? Yeah, like... like that pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.41,0:30:14.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}1961年 约翰·格伦每晚都来这里用餐\N{\rOriginal text}John Glenn ate here every night in '61.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.20,0:30:14.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(沃尔菲上太空了)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.62,0:30:17.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他用我们的一支笔来写飞行手册\N{\rOriginal text}He would work on his flight manuals, and he'd use one of our pens.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.37,0:30:19.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那支笔上过水星6号\N{\rOriginal text}That one ended up on Mercury 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.79,0:30:23.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这里是全世界唯一一家 名字上过太空的餐厅\N{\rOriginal text}You're at the only restaurant in the world whose name's been in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.30,0:30:26.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很酷\N{\rOriginal text}That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.51,0:30:34.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}正前方\N{\rOriginal text}And right up ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.18,0:30:36.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是著名的水星火箭\N{\rOriginal text}it's the famous Mercury rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.93,0:30:39.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一定要在这里拍照 但别站太近\N{\rOriginal text}Be sure to get a picture here, but don't stand too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.94,0:30:41.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}火箭可能会发射\N{\rOriginal text}They might go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.36,0:30:45.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那个周末过后 他就恢复了\N{\rOriginal text}He recovered after that weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.36,0:30:45.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(你能准备好吗? 距离发射还有171天)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.16,0:30:52.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你每次进房间 大家都会安静下来 你感到困扰吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Does it bother you that a room dies every time you walk into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.49,0:30:54.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你该待在你那边的\N{\rOriginal text}You're supposed to stay on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.79,0:30:56.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我想你了\N{\rOriginal text}I missed you. Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.04,0:30:57.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我希望你批准我们新的推广活动\N{\rOriginal text}I'd like you to approve our new ad campaigns.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.79,0:30:59.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不如就像上次一样先斩后奏吧\N{\rOriginal text}Why don't you just sidestep me like you did last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.71,0:31:02.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我想为那些让你措手不及的采访道歉\N{\rOriginal text}I wanna apologize for blindsiding you with the interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.71,0:31:04.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我有办法解决我们的资金问题\N{\rOriginal text}I have a fix for our money problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.42,0:31:09.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不接受你的道歉 也不接受这些莫名奇妙的东西\N{\rOriginal text}Well, your apology is rejected, and so is whatever this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.84,0:31:12.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}欧米茄 听着 这里不是麦迪逊大道\N{\rOriginal text}Omega. Look, this isn't Madison Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.68,0:31:14.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们不会为这种东西买单 不 免费的\N{\rOriginal text}We don't pay for this stuff. No, it's cost-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.85,0:31:16.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}品牌方能得到钱都买不到的合作机会\N{\rOriginal text}The brands get a tie-in money can't buy,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.81,0:31:19.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而国家航空航天局 可以潜移默化去影响普通人\N{\rOriginal text}and NASA works its way into the minds of everyday people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.69,0:31:22.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}手表广告? 这就是你的绝妙点子?\N{\rOriginal text}A watch ad? That's-That's your big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.77,0:31:24.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}准备好了?\N{\rOriginal text}Ready? Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.73,0:31:25.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}牙膏\N{\rOriginal text}Toothpaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.49,0:31:31.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}菓珍 “阿波罗宇航员选择的 能量早餐饮品\N{\rOriginal text}Tang. "The energy breakfast drink chosen for Apollo astronauts
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.36,0:31:33.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}专供登月之旅使用” 月球优惠券?\N{\rOriginal text}on their trip to the moon." Moon coupons?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.66,0:31:36.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我个人最喜欢的要属这个\N{\rOriginal text}But, my personal favorite,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.83,0:31:39.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}鲜果布衣 是吧?\N{\rOriginal text}Fruit of the Loom. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.75,0:31:42.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}宇航员在太空服里面总得穿点什么吧?\N{\rOriginal text}The guys gotta wear something under those big suits, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.29,0:31:43.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}鲜果布衣真的太能代表航天局了\N{\rOriginal text}Nothing says NASA like Fruit of the Loom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.96,0:31:47.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}听着 我不会把飞船变成飞行广告牌\N{\rOriginal text}Look, I am not turning this ship into a flying billboard
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.46,0:31:49.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}无论你多么渴望都不行\N{\rOriginal text}no matter how much you want it to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.38,0:31:52.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}还有 我们没时间在发射前测试这些东西\N{\rOriginal text}And by the way, we don't have time to test all this before liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.14,0:31:54.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们不必真的把这些送上太空 只要说说就好\N{\rOriginal text}We don't have to send any of this up into space as long as we say it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.72,0:31:56.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所以你打算撒谎?\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, so you're gonna lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.14,0:31:58.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这叫推销 我们不会欺骗顾客\N{\rOriginal text}It's called selling. We're not lying to the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.10,0:32:00.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们在改变他们的思维方式 不 这叫撒谎\N{\rOriginal text}We're changing the way they think. No, it's called lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.31,0:32:03.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所有人在你眼里都只是顾客吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Everyone is just a customer to you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.23,0:32:06.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}听着 我知道你是个厉害的广告精英\N{\rOriginal text}Look, I know that you're a big old fancy ad shark and everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.77,0:32:09.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但国家航空航天局 不是能用广告曲和广告词推销的\N{\rOriginal text}but NASA's not something that you sell with a jingle and a slogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.99,0:32:12.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不知道我们是谁\N{\rOriginal text}You do not know who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.41,0:32:14.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}行 好吧 玛格丽特·汉密尔顿是谁?\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, okay. Who's Margaret Hamilton?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.95,0:32:16.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}谁? 她是你的手下\N{\rOriginal text}Who? She works here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.99,0:32:19.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有四十万人和太空计划有关\N{\rOriginal text}There are 400,000 people that are affiliated
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.41,0:32:21.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}琼斯女士 她是你的工程师之一\N{\rOriginal text}with this space program, Ms. Jones. She's one of your engineers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.91,0:32:24.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}乔安·摩根是谁? 她是点火室的\N{\rOriginal text}Who's JoAnn Morgan? She works in the firing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.13,0:32:27.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你问过她当初为什么接这份工作吗? 我就问过\N{\rOriginal text}Did you ever ask her why she took this job in the first place? I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.17,0:32:30.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她说因为她的血液里流的都是火箭燃料\N{\rOriginal text}She says it's because she has rocket fuel in her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.34,0:32:32.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}国家航空航天局不光是个标志 也代表着人民\N{\rOriginal text}And NASA's not just a logo, it's people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.51,0:32:34.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那些每天早上醒来\N{\rOriginal text}People who wake up every morning
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.01,0:32:36.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}决心创造奇迹的人\N{\rOriginal text}and commit to accomplishing the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.60,0:32:39.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}同时跟大家穿着一样的内衣\N{\rOriginal text}And all while wearing the same underwear as the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.89,0:32:43.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}艾拉 你有任何需要吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Ella, can I help you with anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.07,0:32:51.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}谢谢\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.61,0:32:55.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我预估了一下 如果你接受关键赞助\N{\rOriginal text}So I ran the projections, and this is what you stand to make
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.32,0:32:57.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}能赚到这个数\N{\rOriginal text}if you accept key sponsorships.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.62,0:33:02.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们不能收私人的钱\N{\rOriginal text}We-We can't take private money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.50,0:33:04.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}无所谓的 明白吗?\N{\rOriginal text}It doesn't matter, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.37,0:33:06.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我即将让航天局变得非常受欢迎\N{\rOriginal text}I'm about to make NASA so popular
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.17,0:33:09.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}国会终将重新提供资金\N{\rOriginal text}that Congress will finally turn the taps back on around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.00,0:33:12.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只需让阿姆斯特朗 戴上一块欧米茄手表就行?\N{\rOriginal text}And all I have to do is just let Armstrong put on an Omega watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.63,0:33:15.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 如果我们得到资金\N{\rOriginal text}No. If we get the money flowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.18,0:33:17.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那你必须向我证明\N{\rOriginal text}then you've gotta prove to me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.68,0:33:20.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可可海滩也有不错的地方可以吃晚餐\N{\rOriginal text}that Cocoa Beach has a decent place to get dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.40,0:33:29.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}成交 我... 好 成交 太好了 呜呼\N{\rOriginal text}Deal. I... Yes! Deal! Yes! Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.61,0:33:33.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 等等 我得设置底线 手纸不行\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, no, wait. I'm drawing the line at toilet paper though,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.74,0:33:36.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为世人不用知道我们的人用什么擦屁股\N{\rOriginal text}because the world does not get to know what our guys wipe their ass with.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.70,0:33:38.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真臭\N{\rOriginal text}Well, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.54,0:33:45.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你返回地球后想去度假吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Would you like to go for a vacation when you come back to earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.46,0:33:48.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}根据目前的情况看\N{\rOriginal text}The situation being what it is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.13,0:33:50.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我最可能去的地方...\N{\rOriginal text}the place I would most like to go, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.09,0:33:53.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}下次把桌子撤掉 沃尔特\N{\rOriginal text}Lose the table next time, Walter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.05,0:33:55.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼尔看起来 像在做通用电气的季度盈利报告\N{\rOriginal text}Neil looks like he's giving GE's quarterly profit report.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.80,0:33:57.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们一直用这张桌...\N{\rOriginal text}That's always been our table...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.55,0:33:59.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}电视让他们走进人们的起居室\N{\rOriginal text}TV brings them in to people's living rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.43,0:34:01.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们应该看起来像家中的客人\N{\rOriginal text}They should look like they belong there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.01,0:34:03.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那意味着我们成功了\N{\rOriginal text}It'd mean that we succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.43,0:34:06.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你还是负责人 沃尔特 别担心\N{\rOriginal text}You're still in charge, Walter. Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.23,0:34:08.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不过等我帮完忙后\N{\rOriginal text}When I'm done helping though,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.73,0:34:10.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这些人会比披头士乐队还火\N{\rOriginal text}those men are gonna be bigger than The Beatles.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.86,0:34:14.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我可以完成99.9%的登月之旅 我很满意\N{\rOriginal text}I'm getting to go 99.9% of the way there, and that suits me just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.45,0:34:17.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(下一站 月球)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.91,0:34:21.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(阿波罗11号 最危险的航行)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.16,0:34:30.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}家乐氏的那个副总叫什么? 应该是哈里森·德里斯科尔\N{\rOriginal text}What's the name of that VP at Kellogg's? I believe it's Harrison Driscoll.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.16,0:34:26.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(阿波罗登月在即)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.83,0:34:31.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 哈里森\N{\rOriginal text}All right, Harrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.75,0:34:36.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不要用“噼啪 笑笑 泡泡” 改用“尼尔 巴兹和迈克” 不错吧?\N{\rOriginal text}So instead of "Snap, Crackle, Pop," "Neil, Buzz and Mike." It's cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.68,0:34:42.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科尔\N{\rOriginal text}Cole!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.73,0:34:48.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}确保那个不会生锈 亨利 能签一下这些吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Make sure that doesn't rust, Henry. Can you mark these?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.81,0:34:54.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿... 你看见了吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, hey. Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.27,0:34:55.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你没看见那只猫?\N{\rOriginal text}You didn't see the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.45,0:34:59.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}菓珍的瓶子再推近些\N{\rOriginal text}Go closer on the Tang bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.95,0:35:02.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}字体再大些 放上培根和鸡蛋\N{\rOriginal text}Make the font bigger and put bacon with the eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.95,0:35:05.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别忘了 我们推销的是美国\N{\rOriginal text}Let's not forget, we're selling America, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.16,0:35:10.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“彼得潘花生酱 丝滑到飞起 此酱只应天上有”\N{\rOriginal text}"Peter Pan Peanut Butter. Peanut butter that's out-of-this-world smooth."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.42,0:35:13.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“哈苏 以他们的视角看世界”\N{\rOriginal text}"Hasselblad. See the world the way they do."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.71,0:35:15.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拉里 这是欧米茄的好机会\N{\rOriginal text}Larry, this is Omega's big chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.80,0:35:18.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在每一块超霸的背面 直到永远\N{\rOriginal text}On the back of every Speedmaster till the end of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.68,0:35:20.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(宇航员登上月球时将佩戴欧米茄手表)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.55,0:35:23.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“第一块被戴上月球的手表” 对吧?\N{\rOriginal text}"The first watch worn on the moon." Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.39,0:35:25.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}现在我们得把它立起来\N{\rOriginal text}Now we just gotta stand her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.85,0:35:27.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一切都将是值得的\N{\rOriginal text}It's all gonna be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.31,0:35:32.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(美国靠阿波罗11号取得领先)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.57,0:35:39.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿... 你占了我的车位 我们在为凯莉布景\N{\rOriginal text}Hey. Hey! You're in my spot. We're setting up a shot for Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.46,0:35:54.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们的阿波罗11号任务有三位宇航员\N{\rOriginal text}We've got three astronauts on the Apollo 11 mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.09,0:35:57.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们站在三辆漂亮的美国汽车前\N{\rOriginal text}There they are in front of three beautiful American cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.76,0:35:59.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真棒\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, this is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.01,0:36:00.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们必须立刻前往测试楼\N{\rOriginal text}You gotta be in the test facility right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.55,0:36:01.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跟凯莉说\N{\rOriginal text}Talk to Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.51,0:36:03.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉说我们花1块就能开走科尔维特\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly said we could take a Corvette home for a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.39,0:36:04.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你来啦 1美元?\N{\rOriginal text}There you are. A dollar?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.43,0:36:06.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我需要占用他们15分钟而已\N{\rOriginal text}I'm gonna need them for 15 minutes, but that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.18,0:36:08.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我15分钟前就需要他们了 凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}I needed them 15 minutes ago, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.27,0:36:10.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你知道他们穿的宇航服有多贵吗?\N{\rOriginal text}You know how expensive those suits are?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.31,0:36:14.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别担心 他只是发射主管\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, don't worry. It's just the launch director.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.94,0:36:17.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}登月舱的样子很怪 凯利先生 它的原理是什么?\N{\rOriginal text}This strange looking bird, the LEM, Mr. Kelly. How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.98,0:36:20.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是让人\N{\rOriginal text}Well, this is a spacecraft that's used
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.28,0:36:22.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}着陆到月球表面的飞船\N{\rOriginal text}to take men down to the lunar surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.99,0:36:25.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}登月舱里三位宇航员中的两位...\N{\rOriginal text}And two of the three astronauts in the LEM...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.95,0:36:33.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飞行指挥 我们错过了目标 正飘向广袤的虚空\N{\rOriginal text}Flight, we missed target and are drifting into the vast abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.92,0:36:39.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们死了 再来 是\N{\rOriginal text}And we're dead. Again. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.05,0:36:41.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}着陆前30秒耗尽了燃料\N{\rOriginal text}Ran out of fuel 30 seconds before touchdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.22,0:36:42.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 但是着陆本身不错\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, but the landing, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.51,0:36:44.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很顺利 很好 俯仰角度很好 继续\N{\rOriginal text}it was smooth... It was good. Great pitch. Forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.43,0:36:45.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们俩撒谎的技术真烂\N{\rOriginal text}You're both bad liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.89,0:36:49.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼尔 迈克 巴兹 能再为琼斯女士 和欧米茄多拍一张照片吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Neil, Mike, Buzz, if I can get one more photo for Ms. Jones and Omega?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.47,0:36:50.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哥们 你谁啊?\N{\rOriginal text}Who are you, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.77,0:36:55.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 举起手表 小伙子们\N{\rOriginal text}All right, watches up, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.86,0:36:57.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}给欧米茄来个微笑\N{\rOriginal text}And smile for Omega.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.24,0:37:07.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是戴维斯 我打扰到你了吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Davis. Am I interrupting?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.08,0:37:11.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一直在打扰 你面前应该有个盒子\N{\rOriginal text}Always. There should be a box in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.79,0:37:13.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不如打开看看?\N{\rOriginal text}Why don't you open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.71,0:37:20.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}欧米茄感谢你的服务\N{\rOriginal text}Omega thanks you for your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.13,0:37:22.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你的宇航员们在电视上大出风头\N{\rOriginal text}Your boys are all over TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.88,0:37:28.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}资金又开始流入了 所以... 共进晚餐?\N{\rOriginal text}the taps are flowing again. So... dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.85,0:37:33.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 卡纳维拉尔码头 5点\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Canaveral Pier. Five o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.44,0:37:35.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}戴着手表来\N{\rOriginal text}Wear your watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.19,0:37:40.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}下午3点是他们播放采访的 最佳时段 也是最后一个\N{\rOriginal text}3:00 p.m. is their best and final time slot to air the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.36,0:37:43.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}播阿姆斯特朗的独家采访? 下午3点是给小孩和闲人看的\N{\rOriginal text}For an exclusive with Armstrong? 3:00 p.m. is for children and deadbeats.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.70,0:37:46.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们说有战争方面的突发新闻\N{\rOriginal text}They said they have breaking news from the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.37,0:37:50.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}敌军规模未知\N{\rOriginal text}Unknown size enemy force.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.24,0:37:52.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}敌军伤亡人数不详\N{\rOriginal text}Enemy casualties are unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.62,0:37:54.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但大家都看到过到底是怎么回事\N{\rOriginal text}but you've seen how it really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.33,0:37:56.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}让阿波罗任务一直有新闻的努力失败了\N{\rOriginal text}So much for keeping Apollo back in the news cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.46,0:37:58.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}英雄主义 危险 恐惧 全部融为一体\N{\rOriginal text}Heroism, danger, fear, all rolled into one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.92,0:38:00.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}无法用语言形容\N{\rOriginal text}Words don't describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.67,0:38:04.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是哥伦比亚广播公司新闻台的 理查德·思雷尔克德 柬埔寨边境附近报道\N{\rOriginal text}Richard Threlkeld, CBS News. Near the Cambodian border.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.43,0:38:10.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}谢谢你 斯科蒂船长 感谢\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you, Captain Scotty. Appreciate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.31,0:38:12.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.31,0:38:14.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你对女士可真是一毛不拔\N{\rOriginal text}Well, you spare no expense on a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.23,0:38:15.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尝尝看嘛\N{\rOriginal text}Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.64,0:38:17.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}虾 蛋黄酱 面包\N{\rOriginal text}Shrimp, mayo, bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.10,0:38:19.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这恰好是方圆百里之内最美味的一餐\N{\rOriginal text}And that happens to be the best meal in a hundred miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.36,0:38:25.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我没说错吧\N{\rOriginal text}Mmm. Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.61,0:38:28.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我怎么不知道这地方?\N{\rOriginal text}How'd I not know about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.24,0:38:30.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不是所有人都喜欢打广告\N{\rOriginal text}Not everybody likes to advertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.16,0:38:33.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}说得妙 有两下子嘛\N{\rOriginal text}Nice one. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.21,0:38:41.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是火箭发射的地方 就是那里\N{\rOriginal text}That's where the rocket will launch out of. Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.09,0:38:48.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你戴那块手表戴可真好看 你戴着很合适\N{\rOriginal text}That watch looks great on you. You wear it very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.18,0:38:53.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}谢谢\N{\rOriginal text}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.39,0:38:59.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那天晚上我在酒吧里跟你说...\N{\rOriginal text}That night at the bar, what I said to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.85,0:39:01.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你的目光无法从我身上挪开\N{\rOriginal text}That you couldn't take your eyes off me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.48,0:39:03.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是你见过最美的女人\N{\rOriginal text}and I was the most beautiful woman that you'd ever seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.86,0:39:06.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 就是这句 这... 对\N{\rOriginal text}Y-Yeah, that part. That... Yes. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.94,0:39:08.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是我冲动了\N{\rOriginal text}It was impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.49,0:39:11.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是对陌生人说的话 可我们现在共事了\N{\rOriginal text}It was meant for a stranger, and we're working together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.45,0:39:13.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只是不希望你认为我...\N{\rOriginal text}So, I just don't want you to think that I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.87,0:39:14.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对我有意思?\N{\rOriginal text}Interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.25,0:39:18.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只是想把话说清楚\N{\rOriginal text}I just wanted to clear the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.17,0:39:21.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好的 说得很清楚\N{\rOriginal text}Oh. Well, the air was clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.83,0:39:22.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很好\N{\rOriginal text}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.38,0:39:33.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我有个想法 对 那话只适用30秒\N{\rOriginal text}I had a thought. Yeah. It was perfect for 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.10,0:39:35.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有哪个电视网是全天候报道的?\N{\rOriginal text}What are the networks covering night and day?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.81,0:39:37.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你觉得我有时间看电视吗?\N{\rOriginal text}You think I have time to watch TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.93,0:39:41.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}越南 他们直接从前线报道\N{\rOriginal text}Vietnam. They're broadcasting straight from the action.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.19,0:39:43.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人们已经不想只听新闻了\N{\rOriginal text}And people don't want to just hear the news anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.02,0:39:44.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们想直击新闻现场\N{\rOriginal text}They wanna see it in the making.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.65,0:39:46.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.16,0:39:56.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不妨就让他们看\N{\rOriginal text}Why not let 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.16,0:39:56.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(登月现场直播 阿波罗11号)
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.29,0:39:58.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你想在登月舱里放个电视直播摄像机?\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, you want to put a live television camera on the LEM?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.79,0:40:00.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的\N{\rOriginal text}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.04,0:40:01.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我的人在太空里努力活命\N{\rOriginal text}My guys are trying to survive up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.67,0:40:03.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没时间学如何拍电影\N{\rOriginal text}They don't have time to figure out how to film a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.63,0:40:06.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们替他们学 他们只需对准目标拍摄即可\N{\rOriginal text}We'll figure it out for 'em. All they have to do is point and shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.13,0:40:08.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不明白 这是后勤方面的噩梦\N{\rOriginal text}You don't get it. It's a logistical nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.51,0:40:11.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}问题涉及电力 储存空间 重量\N{\rOriginal text}There's power issues, storage, weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.26,0:40:13.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}甚至没有摄像机能在太空里工作\N{\rOriginal text}There's not even a camera that would work up there
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.18,0:40:16.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为夜晚温度是零下129摄氏度 白天超过121摄氏度\N{\rOriginal text}'cause it's negative 200 degrees at night and over 250 degrees during the daytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.31,0:40:18.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你能想象看直播的情景吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Can you imagine seeing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.52,0:40:21.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不能 我刚说了这不可能\N{\rOriginal text}No. I just said it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.98,0:40:23.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 这就是重点\N{\rOriginal text}Yes. That's the point. Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.73,0:40:25.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这将是有史以来最伟大的电视节目\N{\rOriginal text}It would be the greatest televised event ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.82,0:40:27.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你认为这是个综艺节目吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you think this is a game show?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.15,0:40:29.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}苏联人没有播出\N{\rOriginal text}There is a very good reason
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.82,0:40:32.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们在太空行走是有充分理由的\N{\rOriginal text}why the Soviets aren't broadcasting their space walks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.66,0:40:34.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为苏联是守口如瓶的独裁政权国\N{\rOriginal text}Because they're a tight-lipped dictatorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.70,0:40:35.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 我们不是 天啊\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, that's not us. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.99,0:40:38.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们取得成功 是举国成功\N{\rOriginal text}When we succeed, we do it as a nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.04,0:40:40.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们遭遇失败 是举国悲痛 对\N{\rOriginal text}And when we fail, we grieve as a nation. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.41,0:40:42.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这就是作为美国人的意义所在\N{\rOriginal text}That's what it means to be American.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.21,0:40:44.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别跟我说作为美国人意味着什么\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, stop telling me what it means to be an American.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.75,0:40:47.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们当中只有一个人一辈子在报效祖国\N{\rOriginal text}There's only one of us here that has served their country their entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.59,0:40:53.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉 登月舱里不会放摄像机的\N{\rOriginal text}I'm sorry. We're not putting the camera on the LEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.56,0:41:00.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是认真的 不放\N{\rOriginal text}I mean it. We're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.06,0:41:04.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们会放的\N{\rOriginal text}We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.94,0:41:08.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(压力点)
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.57,0:41:12.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没有更多燃料 他不可能成功\N{\rOriginal text}There's no way he can do it without more fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.57,0:41:18.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}让他再测一次 好\N{\rOriginal text}Have him run it again. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.08,0:41:27.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我时间很紧 什么事?\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. [sighs] I'm on a tight schedule. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.29,0:41:31.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉跟我说了摄像机的点子 我们很喜欢\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly briefed me on the camera idea, and we like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.26,0:41:33.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常喜欢\N{\rOriginal text}We like it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.22,0:41:35.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她说错了 我们做不到\N{\rOriginal text}She misspoke. We can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.14,0:41:38.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}根本没有这种科技\N{\rOriginal text}There is no such technology that even exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.51,0:41:40.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}其实有 你知道吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Actually it does. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.72,0:41:43.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是国防部设计的\N{\rOriginal text}The Department of Defense designed this
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.89,0:41:47.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}为了夜间寻找在越南被击落的飞行员\N{\rOriginal text}to find downed fighter pilots in Vietnam at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.31,0:41:51.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}听着 这是机密 但国防部会给你使用\N{\rOriginal text}Now, it's classified but the DOD is going to let you use it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.94,0:41:53.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}只要没人知道它是什么即可\N{\rOriginal text}as long as nobody knows what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.78,0:41:55.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}绝对没有空间装这么重的设备\N{\rOriginal text}There's absolutely no space for equipment that heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.95,0:41:57.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}老天 我们连螺丝钉都称重\N{\rOriginal text}We are weighing screws for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.70,0:41:59.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什么... 这也就7公斤吧\N{\rOriginal text}What... I mean, what is this, 15 pounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.58,0:42:01.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 那就用轻一些的螺丝钉\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. So, just, like, lighter screws.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.45,0:42:03.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们在试用另一个燃料单元\N{\rOriginal text}We're trying for another fuel cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.37,0:42:08.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好让我们的人登月后 依然有足够的燃料发射\N{\rOriginal text}So our men, when they get to the moon, they still have enough fuel to lift off.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.17,0:42:11.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她所有的馊主意当中 这个是最糟糕的\N{\rOriginal text}Out of all her bad ideas, this one is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.42,0:42:14.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}其实总统很喜欢这个点子\N{\rOriginal text}Actually, the president loves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.84,0:42:17.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所以现在这就是个好主意\N{\rOriginal text}So, now it's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.43,0:42:20.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我跟你用简单的话说吧 科尔\N{\rOriginal text}So, let me put it to you simply, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.14,0:42:22.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}找个办法把这东西放进那东西\N{\rOriginal text}Find a way to put this on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.89,0:42:25.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是命令 顶头老大下达的\N{\rOriginal text}This is an order. From the tippy top.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.57,0:42:40.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}唐 斯图 请到这里来\N{\rOriginal text}Don, Stu. Can you come in here, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.58,0:42:46.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}谢谢 别什么事都闹别扭\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you. Let's not make everything so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.92,0:42:52.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请帮琼斯小姐把这个绝密摄像机拆出来\N{\rOriginal text}Please help Miss Jones strip this top secret camera down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.17,0:42:54.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不希望他们知道这是绝密\N{\rOriginal text}I don't want 'em to know it's top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.34,0:42:55.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}现在他们知道了\N{\rOriginal text}Well, now they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.42,0:42:57.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请把这个绝密摄像机拆出来\N{\rOriginal text}Please strip this top secret camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.26,0:43:00.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}装在登月舱上 以备直播\N{\rOriginal text}Mount it onto the LEM for live broadcasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.80,0:43:04.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科尔 还有一件事\N{\rOriginal text}Cole. One last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.35,0:43:09.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}上周 一架中情局的间谍飞机拍到几张\N{\rOriginal text}Last week, a CIA spy plane took some surveillance photographs
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.31,0:43:12.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}苏联新型N1火箭的照片\N{\rOriginal text}of the new Russian N1 rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.11,0:43:13.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}国会看到了\N{\rOriginal text}And Congress saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.82,0:43:16.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有些议员对最后一轮拨款\N{\rOriginal text}and some of the members are having cold feet
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.69,0:43:19.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}产生了疑虑\N{\rOriginal text}about the final round of funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.36,0:43:21.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们还有好几个月才能赢下登月竞赛\N{\rOriginal text}We're months away from winning this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.28,0:43:23.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我会让他们来这里参观\N{\rOriginal text}I'm gonna send them down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.03,0:43:25.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你要说服他们稍安勿躁\N{\rOriginal text}and you're gonna convince them to sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.08,0:43:28.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 我... 来写几个和他们谈话的要点\N{\rOriginal text}No. I'm... I'm gonna write up some talking points.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.63,0:43:39.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别往心里去\N{\rOriginal text}Don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.76,0:43:43.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飞行员和重力对抗 这是他们的天性\N{\rOriginal text}Pilots fight gravity. It's part of their nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.45,0:44:06.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}亨利?\N{\rOriginal text}Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.71,0:44:13.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 很高兴你不是科尔\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I'm... I'm glad you're not Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.67,0:44:14.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是\N{\rOriginal text}Oh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.25,0:44:16.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他不喜欢我吸烟\N{\rOriginal text}He don't like me smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.92,0:44:18.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎么 你怕他会给你下禁足令?\N{\rOriginal text}What, are you worried he's gonna ground you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.76,0:44:26.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 我... 去年做了紧急搭桥手术\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, no. I, uh... I had emergency bypass surgery last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.26,0:44:29.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 那个混蛋非常顽固 非要我活下去\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. That son of a bitch. He's hell-bent on keeping me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.81,0:44:31.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉 我不知道\N{\rOriginal text}I'm sorry. I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.52,0:44:33.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 这里没人知道\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Nobody here does.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.44,0:44:34.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}除了科尔\N{\rOriginal text}Just Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.44,0:44:40.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 他到医院来 安慰了我太太三天\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. He came to the hospital and held my wife's hand for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.32,0:44:44.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的 我们认识很久了\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. It's a long way from the day we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.12,0:44:49.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}当时那小子刚从朝鲜回来\N{\rOriginal text}Kid had just got back from Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.12,0:44:53.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是空军最优秀的飞行员\N{\rOriginal text}The top pilot in the Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.08,0:44:56.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}银星勋章 飞行十字勋章\N{\rOriginal text}Silver Star. Flying Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.67,0:45:01.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们当时选宇航员时 他在爱德华兹空军基地是头号人选\N{\rOriginal text}He was first in line at Edwards when they were looking for astronauts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.30,0:45:04.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但他最后没能入选\N{\rOriginal text}But, uh, he ended up not making the cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.43,0:45:10.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}为什么? 是他的脾气吧\N{\rOriginal text}So, what got him? It was his temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.39,0:45:14.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不... 是他的心脏\N{\rOriginal text}No, no. His heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.48,0:45:15.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}医生发现他有心房颤动\N{\rOriginal text}Doc found an A-fib.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.86,0:45:20.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这个小毛病足以让他无法参加太空计划\N{\rOriginal text}A little thing but enough to keep him out of the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.74,0:45:24.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}最优秀的飞行员科尔·戴维斯 却永远无法上太空\N{\rOriginal text}Cole Davis is the best pilot who will never get to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.13,0:45:43.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我在过去15年里天天看这个景色\N{\rOriginal text}You know, I've been looking at this view every day for the last 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.34,0:45:48.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但最近我有种第一次看到的感觉\N{\rOriginal text}But lately, it's like I'm seeing it for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.85,0:45:54.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗1号给这里留下了巨大的阴影\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 1 cast a big shadow on this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.69,0:46:00.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}重新看到一些光明真好\N{\rOriginal text}It's nice to have some light back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.28,0:46:05.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.58,0:46:12.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 我总看到科尔每天晚上开车去那边\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, I keep seeing Cole drive out there every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.58,0:46:15.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他在做什么?\N{\rOriginal text}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.59,0:46:20.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}做园艺\N{\rOriginal text}Gardening.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.19,0:47:22.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(34号发射场)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.19,0:47:25.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(阿波罗1号乘组的精神永垂不朽)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.92,0:47:43.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}准备好了吗? 好了\N{\rOriginal text}You ready? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.55,0:47:52.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 听着 我们... 带参议员参观一下\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Look, we just... We give the senator a tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.89,0:47:56.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们好好哄他30分钟 把这个地方运营下去\N{\rOriginal text}We play nice for 30 minutes. We keep the lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.27,0:47:58.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 行吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.81,0:48:01.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎么了? 它在那里\N{\rOriginal text}What? She's just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.60,0:48:02.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别... 跑 不...\N{\rOriginal text}Don't run. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.77,0:48:04.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}千万别跑 别... 等等 闭嘴\N{\rOriginal text}Just don't run. Don't... Wait. [shushing] Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.65,0:48:06.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 你看 你把它吓跑了\N{\rOriginal text}No. See, you scared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.78,0:48:07.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我刚吃过东西\N{\rOriginal text}I just ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.99,0:48:16.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}亨利 快...\N{\rOriginal text}Henry, come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.46,0:48:22.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我讨厌那只猫\N{\rOriginal text}I hate that cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.67,0:48:25.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我懂你的意思\N{\rOriginal text}I see what y... you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.09,0:48:28.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这... 猫真讨厌 你看到它看我的眼神了吗?\N{\rOriginal text}That's an asshole cat. Did you see the look it gave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.63,0:48:30.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}它在嘲讽我\N{\rOriginal text}It's just taunting me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.47,0:48:33.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是什么? 是猫食\N{\rOriginal text}What is that? That's cat food.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.85,0:48:36.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有人在喂它 是谁?\N{\rOriginal text}Somebody's feeding that thing. Who's doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.10,0:48:38.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}找出来 立刻查出是谁 立刻炒掉\N{\rOriginal text}Find them. [pants] Find them immediately, and fire them immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.98,0:48:41.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}戴维斯先生 长官 霍普参议员来了\N{\rOriginal text}Mr. Davis. Sir, uh, Senator Hopp is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.56,0:48:43.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 怎么了? 你看起来很帅\N{\rOriginal text}All right. What? You look fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.27,0:48:44.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}参议员\N{\rOriginal text}Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.94,0:48:46.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你好 戴维斯先生 参议员 我很荣幸\N{\rOriginal text}Hello, Mr. Davis. Senator. What an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.73,0:48:49.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我很荣幸 幸会 先生 幸会\N{\rOriginal text}It's an honor and a pleasure. Very nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.36,0:48:54.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗11号太空舱已经运达\N{\rOriginal text}Well, the Apollo 11 capsule has arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.37,0:48:57.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}下周 我们会把它装在土星5号火箭上\N{\rOriginal text}and next week, we will be attaching it to the Saturn V rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.83,0:49:01.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也就是发射升空 带我们离开地球大气层的那个火箭\N{\rOriginal text}And that gets us off the ground and out of earth's atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.04,0:49:05.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这些都很了不起 但我得直说\N{\rOriginal text}Well, that's all very impressive, but I have to be up-front.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.84,0:49:09.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}佐治亚州今年洪水泛滥\N{\rOriginal text}Georgia had some devastating floods this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.13,0:49:12.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要投票把这笔钱用于赈灾\N{\rOriginal text}And I'm voting to put this money toward our relief fund.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.47,0:49:14.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这似乎有点自私 不是吗?\N{\rOriginal text}That seems a little selfish, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.05,0:49:16.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你说什么? 就是一种说法\N{\rOriginal text}Excuse me? Uh, that's a figure of speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.97,0:49:19.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他是这个意思 我的大多数投票人认为\N{\rOriginal text}Here's what he means. My voters mostly think
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.60,0:49:22.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们在登月计划上花费过多\N{\rOriginal text}we are overspending on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.23,0:49:23.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有意思 因为当我... 哟呼\N{\rOriginal text}That's funny, because... Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.85,0:49:25.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不好意思 霍普参议员\N{\rOriginal text}Excuse me. Senator Hopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.94,0:49:28.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你可能不记得我了\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, you probably don't remember me,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.36,0:49:31.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但你在我大二时来我学校做过演讲\N{\rOriginal text}but you spoke at my sophomore year of college.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.53,0:49:33.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}佐治亚理工学院 1955级\N{\rOriginal text}Georgia Tech. '55.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.70,0:49:34.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你是个大黄蜂校友?\N{\rOriginal text}You're a Buzz?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.95,0:49:37.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的 先生 我当然记得\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, sir. Of course I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.08,0:49:39.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那天 你的话激励了我\N{\rOriginal text}Your words inspired me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.29,0:49:43.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你说“承诺意味着忠于一项事业”\N{\rOriginal text}You said, "Commitment means staying loyal to a cause."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.21,0:49:46.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}两年后 我以优异的成绩毕业 现在我负责这个部门\N{\rOriginal text}Two years later, I graduated with honors. Now I run this department.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.42,0:49:50.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}1962年 你曾说过 你无论如何\N{\rOriginal text}You know, in '62 you said that you would fight
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.13,0:49:53.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}都会为肯尼迪的梦想而奋斗\N{\rOriginal text}for Kennedy's dream no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.17,0:49:56.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我知道登月任务在当时比现在受欢迎\N{\rOriginal text}I know that the moon mission was more popular back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.22,0:49:59.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但如果那个激励我 在国家航空航天局工作的人\N{\rOriginal text}but it would be just a shame
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.35,0:50:03.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没能照当年的那些话去做\N{\rOriginal text}if the man whose words inspired me to work at NASA
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.60,0:50:06.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就太可惜了\N{\rOriginal text}didn't live by those very same words.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.69,0:50:12.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那就太可惜了 不是吗? 先生 你真是个了不起的人\N{\rOriginal text}It would be a shame, wouldn't it? Sir, you are just such a wonderful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.86,0:50:14.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常感谢\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you so much. Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.03,0:50:15.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你真了不起\N{\rOriginal text}You are a wonderful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.41,0:50:17.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她可真是个佐治亚州甜心美女\N{\rOriginal text}Isn't she just a wonderful Georgia peach here?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.49,0:50:18.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 是\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, my. Oh. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.57,0:50:20.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你嘴真甜 是的\N{\rOriginal text}You are so sweet. Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.74,0:50:24.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我带你来一次贵宾级的参观吧 这是他们的保密项目\N{\rOriginal text}Let me take you on the special VIP tour they didn't tell you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.75,0:50:26.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好啊 太好了\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, I'd love that. Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.71,0:50:28.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你会陪我一起参观吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you go on this tour with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.71,0:50:30.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}当然会\N{\rOriginal text}I absolutely will.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.25,0:50:31.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你真好\N{\rOriginal text}That's so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.88,0:50:33.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她都热泪盈眶了 真吓人\N{\rOriginal text}She teared up. I mean, it's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.63,0:50:36.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}挥手微笑\N{\rOriginal text}Wave and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.01,0:50:39.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜拜\N{\rOriginal text}Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.56,0:50:45.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}太空计划不光臃肿又混乱\N{\rOriginal text}The space program is not only a bloated mess,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.39,0:50:49.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗号还是对上帝\N{\rOriginal text}but Apollo flies in the face of our creator
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.40,0:50:53.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}和我国国父的不敬 我想提醒大家 我们不...\N{\rOriginal text}and the true father of this country. I would remind you that we don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.61,0:50:58.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们搞定了霍普 还需要两票 看起来不会是范宁了\N{\rOriginal text}We landed Hopp. We need two more votes. Looks like it's not gonna be Vanning.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.57,0:51:02.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}绝对不是范宁 接下来是库克参议员\N{\rOriginal text}Definitely not Vanning. Next, we have Senator Cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.20,0:51:04.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}库克有点吓人 我实话实说\N{\rOriginal text}Cook's a little scary. I'm not gonna lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.04,0:51:05.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他是冷战时期的保守派\N{\rOriginal text}He's a Cold War conservative.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.91,0:51:10.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他担心我们的预算 会从国防部的武器研发经费里出\N{\rOriginal text}He's worried that our budget takes away from weapons development at the DOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.25,0:51:14.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 参议员 有了N1火箭\N{\rOriginal text}Now, Senator, with the N1 rocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.30,0:51:16.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}苏联人还是有可能抢在我们前面登月\N{\rOriginal text}the Russians still could land on the moon before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.72,0:51:18.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们接下来要向你展示的最新情报\N{\rOriginal text}What we're about to show you is our most recent intel
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.76,0:51:20.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是他们登月后计划建造的东西\N{\rOriginal text}on what they plan to build if they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.02,0:51:28.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这些是照片? 不是 先生\N{\rOriginal text}And these are photos? No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.31,0:51:31.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是概念画 描绘可能的未来\N{\rOriginal text}Those are, uh, renderings of a possible future.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.40,0:51:32.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}未来的照片?\N{\rOriginal text}Future photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.15,0:51:37.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是个激光炮?\N{\rOriginal text}Is that a laser?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.15,0:51:39.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}它正对着地球开火 先生\N{\rOriginal text}It's going towards earth, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.03,0:51:42.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}它叫什么? “要你命月球激光大杀器” 先生\N{\rOriginal text}What are they calling it? "Killer Lunar Laser Eliminator," sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.74,0:51:46.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“要你命月球激光大杀器”? 是 先生\N{\rOriginal text}"Killer Lunar Laser Eliminator"? Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.71,0:51:48.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}见鬼 厉害了\N{\rOriginal text}Damn it. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.71,0:51:51.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}最后还有赫奇斯参议员\N{\rOriginal text}And, finally, we have Senator Hedges.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.17,0:51:53.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他一直是阿波罗的粉丝\N{\rOriginal text}Now, he's always been a fan of Apollo,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.42,0:51:57.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但州政党给他施压 叫他不得拨款\N{\rOriginal text}but he's getting pressure from his state party not to fund.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.72,0:52:00.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他连呼吸都要对着媒体的镜头\N{\rOriginal text}He can't take in oxygen without a camera pointed at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.34,0:52:03.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那我们就去请点扛摄像机的朋友来\N{\rOriginal text}and we're about to have a few of those around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.85,0:52:05.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有什么问题吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.01,0:52:06.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没有 女士\N{\rOriginal text}No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.81,0:52:08.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那我们去搞定他吧\N{\rOriginal text}Well, let's get him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.35,0:52:12.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大家好\N{\rOriginal text}Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.40,0:52:17.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}先生们\N{\rOriginal text}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.49,0:52:20.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 很高兴能故地重游 各位\N{\rOriginal text}It's... It's... It's great to be back, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.61,0:52:23.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们知道我有多喜欢阿波罗计划\N{\rOriginal text}You know how much I love the Apollo program.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.04,0:52:30.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}参议员 阿波罗10号只会绕月飞行\N{\rOriginal text}Senator. Apollo 10 will just be orbiting the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.71,0:52:34.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但能给我们带来 11号在月球着陆的关键信息\N{\rOriginal text}But it's gonna get us information critical for the touchdown of 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.29,0:52:36.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}比如着陆条件和地点 了不起\N{\rOriginal text}Like landing conditions and location. Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.59,0:52:39.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们为你准备了专座 参议员 在你的支持者中间\N{\rOriginal text}And we've a special seat for you here, Senator, amongst your fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.09,0:52:40.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}为我吗? 谢谢\N{\rOriginal text}For me? Oh. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.34,0:52:44.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗发射控制中心 现在可以开始\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo launch control, and we are go on the countdown
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.72,0:52:47.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗10号登月任务的倒计时了\N{\rOriginal text}for the Apollo 10 lunar mission at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.56,0:52:53.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}点火程序启动\N{\rOriginal text}We have ignition sequence start.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.90,0:52:57.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}五 四 三 二...\N{\rOriginal text}Five, four, three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.44,0:53:00.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所有引擎启动\N{\rOriginal text}All engines running.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.87,0:53:10.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}发射 火箭升空\N{\rOriginal text}Liftoff. We have liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.62,0:53:12.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}现在是整点后49分\N{\rOriginal text}Forty-nine minutes past the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.25,0:53:15.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}发射塔已分离...\N{\rOriginal text}Tower clear. Tower clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.04,0:53:17.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}休斯敦 交给你了\N{\rOriginal text}Houston, she's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.86,0:53:45.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}壮观的发射 我都等不及回来看阿波罗11号了\N{\rOriginal text}Glorious launch. Can't wait to be right back here for Apollo 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.45,0:53:48.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们非常感谢你的支持 参议员\N{\rOriginal text}We cannot thank you enough for your support, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.03,0:53:50.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有件事会麻烦你们一下\N{\rOriginal text}It's gonna cost you more than a pair of binoculars.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.37,0:53:53.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我欠老家做新闻的人一个人情\N{\rOriginal text}I owe a favor to the news fellas back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.62,0:53:57.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我希望你能接受他们的出镜采访\N{\rOriginal text}I'd like you to give them an on-camera interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.63,0:54:01.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}参议员 我是最不适合出镜的人了\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, Senator, I'm the very last person that you want in front of a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.01,0:54:03.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 不接受采访的\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, I d... I don't do interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.09,0:54:06.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但为你可以破例 赫奇斯参议员 我们很乐意\N{\rOriginal text}Except for you, Senator Hedges. We would be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.39,0:54:08.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这女士很机智\N{\rOriginal text}Smart lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.93,0:54:11.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}晚安 晚安\N{\rOriginal text}Good night. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.64,0:54:15.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.27,0:54:17.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没事的\N{\rOriginal text}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.94,0:54:20.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一切尽在掌握\N{\rOriginal text}Got it all under control. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.99,0:54:27.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(好样的 阿波罗)
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.43,0:54:50.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 嘿\N{\rOriginal text}Hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.93,0:54:52.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你也可以休息一晚的\N{\rOriginal text}You're entitled to a night off too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.81,0:54:56.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我若休息 那就是睡觉\N{\rOriginal text}If I am, it's to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.31,0:54:58.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你真的有家吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, you actually have a house?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.44,0:55:00.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我还以为你在办公室睡呢\N{\rOriginal text}I thought you slept at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.15,0:55:04.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 通常是 但... 我有时和珍妮一起睡\N{\rOriginal text}Well, yeah. Usually. But, uh... Well, I mean, sometimes I sleep with Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.82,0:55:08.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 是 她一定很棒\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, yeah. Right. Oh. I'm sure she's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.28,0:55:10.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}珍妮吗? 对 确实\N{\rOriginal text}Jenny? Yeah. She... She is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.16,0:55:15.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}想认识一下吗?\N{\rOriginal text}You wanna meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.91,0:55:17.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好啊 好 珍妮会喜欢你的 来\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Yeah. She'll love you. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.93,0:55:31.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}珍妮 这是凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}Jenny. Jenny, uh, this is Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.68,0:55:33.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉 这就是珍妮\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly, meet Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.10,0:55:36.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跟我战争中开的那架一样\N{\rOriginal text}She's just like the one I flew in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.23,0:55:40.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我把它放在这里 方便在周末开出去兜兜风 省时间\N{\rOriginal text}Keep her here so I can get my flight hours on the weekends. Saves time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.02,0:55:44.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很漂亮\N{\rOriginal text}She's quite a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.86,0:55:46.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. She is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.07,0:55:51.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}想飞一圈吗? 不了\N{\rOriginal text}Wanna go up? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.57,0:55:52.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你确定? 确定\N{\rOriginal text}You sure? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.49,0:55:55.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 来吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.45,0:55:57.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我带你看第二美的景色\N{\rOriginal text}Show you the second-best view.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.80,0:56:15.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}看见那些深色的部分了吗? 看见了\N{\rOriginal text}You see those dark parts there? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.18,0:56:16.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们称之为“月海”\N{\rOriginal text}We call them the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.56,0:56:19.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}月海里的重力更强一些 所以...\N{\rOriginal text}The gravity is stronger in the seas, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.98,0:56:23.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们研究过在每一片月海里着陆的情况\N{\rOriginal text}We've looked to land in, uh, pretty much every single one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.61,0:56:25.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有澄海\N{\rOriginal text}You got the Sea of Serenity.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.69,0:56:28.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}危海 我们很快便排除了这个\N{\rOriginal text}Sea of Crises. We crossed that one off the list pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.82,0:56:30.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 这个名字不利于宣传\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. That's bad PR.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.53,0:56:34.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们最后决定在宁静海着陆\N{\rOriginal text}And then we finally settled on, uh, the Sea of Tranquility.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.66,0:56:36.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是最佳地点\N{\rOriginal text}That's the sweet spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.33,0:56:42.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这么一想 我... 对月球的了解\N{\rOriginal text}You know, come to think about it, I... I know a lot more about the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.75,0:56:45.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}远远超过我对你的了解\N{\rOriginal text}than I know about you by a long shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.71,0:56:48.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我甚至不知道你是哪里人\N{\rOriginal text}I don't even know where you're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.63,0:56:51.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}堪萨斯\N{\rOriginal text}Kansas.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.18,0:56:55.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}来自堪萨斯的凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly from Kansas.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.31,0:56:58.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}堪萨斯的凯莉 你是怎么进入广告这一行的?\N{\rOriginal text}How'd you get into advertising, Kelly from Kansas?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.10,0:57:06.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我爸爸离开时我四岁 妈妈失去了房子\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, well, I was four when my dad left, and my mom lost the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.27,0:57:07.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们住在汽车里\N{\rOriginal text}We lived in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.11,0:57:12.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一个教堂给了她一份卖曲奇罐的工作\N{\rOriginal text}And... a church gave her a job selling cookie tins.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.91,0:57:19.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所以她想了个点子 如果由我挨家挨户推销就能卖出更多\N{\rOriginal text}So, she had this idea that we'd sell more if it was me going door-to-door.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.08,0:57:21.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是啊 聪明的女士\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, yeah. Smart lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.25,0:57:27.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}曲奇罐 然后卖吸尘器 我长大些就转而卖美容用品\N{\rOriginal text}Cookie tins, then it was vacuums, then beauty goods when I got older.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.71,0:57:30.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的 我和我妈周游全国\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Traveling the country, me and my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.88,0:57:33.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们的生活就是这样重回正轨的\N{\rOriginal text}It's how we got back on our feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.01,0:57:37.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我很遗憾你不得不经历这些\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I'm sorry you went through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.35,0:57:43.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不必 我...\N{\rOriginal text}Well, don't be. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.52,0:57:47.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 我很小就学会了如何生存\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. I learned early on how to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.94,0:57:54.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而且家家都有本难念的经\N{\rOriginal text}Plus, we all have our share of tough breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.08,0:58:01.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}亨利跟我说了 心房颤动和你被计划除名的事\N{\rOriginal text}Henry told me about the A-fib and you getting kicked out of the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.08,0:58:05.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我得去跟亨利聊聊\N{\rOriginal text}Hmm. I'm gonna have to have a little conversation with Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.13,0:58:12.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不过我并不完全赞同你的说法\N{\rOriginal text}You know, I don't totally agree with you though.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.72,0:58:18.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎么讲? 我就是不...\N{\rOriginal text}How's that? Well, I just don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.18,0:58:22.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不认为我们的悲伤故事\N{\rOriginal text}I don't think that our sad stories are supposed to
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.23,0:58:23.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就该教会我们如何在世上生存\N{\rOriginal text}teach us how to survive the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.52,0:58:27.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我认为它们应该激励我们去改变世界\N{\rOriginal text}I think they're supposed to make us wanna change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.65,0:58:31.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科尔\N{\rOriginal text}Hmm. Cole!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.73,0:58:34.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}巴兹正在试图短路发动你的科迈罗\N{\rOriginal text}Buzz is trying to hot-wire your Camaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.15,0:58:36.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜托 天啊\N{\rOriginal text}Come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.82,0:58:38.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那么...\N{\rOriginal text}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.91,0:58:41.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你最好去阻止他\N{\rOriginal text}You better go stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.25,0:58:44.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.60,0:59:02.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(卫星汽车旅馆)
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.23,0:59:09.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}老天\N{\rOriginal text}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.56,0:59:11.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们得谈谈\N{\rOriginal text}We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.19,0:59:18.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿凯 你的工作做得十分出色\N{\rOriginal text}You have done outstanding work, Kel.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.70,0:59:20.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}公众的兴趣大大提高了\N{\rOriginal text}Public interest is way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.33,0:59:25.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你搞定了参议员们 确保发射能顺利进行\N{\rOriginal text}You landed the senators and secured the launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.96,0:59:28.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所以你就闯进我的旅店房间?\N{\rOriginal text}And that's why you broke into my motel room?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.00,0:59:29.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}作为感谢吗?\N{\rOriginal text}As a thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.25,0:59:31.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}现在我们知道全世界都会盯着我们看\N{\rOriginal text}Now that we know the whole world will be watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.67,0:59:33.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们不容有失\N{\rOriginal text}we can't afford to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.51,0:59:40.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们必须准备好呈献一个备用版本的\N{\rOriginal text}We need to be prepared to present an alternate version
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.18,0:59:41.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}登月任务\N{\rOriginal text}of the moon landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.06,0:59:44.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一个备用版本?\N{\rOriginal text}An alternate version?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.14,0:59:47.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿尔忒弥斯版本\N{\rOriginal text}The... Artemis version.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.81,0:59:53.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她是阿波罗的孪生姐姐 也就是“备胎”\N{\rOriginal text}She was the twin sister of Apollo, uh, you know, the backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.81,0:59:53.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(绝密 阿尔忒弥斯计划)
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.02,0:59:57.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们必须准备好拍一个小短片\N{\rOriginal text}So we just need to be ready to shoot a little picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.53,1:00:02.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}向人们展示宇航员在月球上行走\N{\rOriginal text}Something showing us, you know, up there walking around,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.16,1:00:03.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}朝镜头挥手\N{\rOriginal text}waving at the camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.95,1:00:07.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你是说作假? 如果一切顺利 短片永远也用不上\N{\rOriginal text}You mean, to fake it? All goes well, we never use it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.37,1:00:09.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但万一...\N{\rOriginal text}But if not...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.67,1:00:16.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你知道我为什么从没坐过牢吗?\N{\rOriginal text}You know why I never went to prison?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.51,1:00:20.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大概知道 但你说吧\N{\rOriginal text}Probably, but humor me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.22,1:00:21.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为我见好就收\N{\rOriginal text}'Cause I quit while I'm ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.43,1:00:24.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这么大的事没法保密 这里有成千上万的员工\N{\rOriginal text}Can't keep a secret this big. Thousands of people work here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.18,1:00:31.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也有成千上万人 在一个沙漠中的保密地点工作\N{\rOriginal text}Well, thousands of people work at a classified location in the desert
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.85,1:00:35.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们在对一个外星飞行器舰队做实验\N{\rOriginal text}that experiments on a fleet of extraterrestrial pods
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.98,1:00:38.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是我们从海底捞上来的\N{\rOriginal text}that we found at the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.44,1:00:41.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你从来没听说过吧?\N{\rOriginal text}And you never heard about that, did ya?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.11,1:00:44.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜托 没这回事\N{\rOriginal text}Come on, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.08,1:00:48.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也许没有 也许有\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, maybe it is, maybe it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.29,1:00:51.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但有一件事是可以肯定的\N{\rOriginal text}But the one thing you can be sure of
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.12,1:00:57.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}全世界都将看到美国人 在月球上插上美国国旗\N{\rOriginal text}is that the world will watch Americans plant an American flag on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.09,1:01:01.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你是说尼克松总统支持这么干?\N{\rOriginal text}And you are telling me that President Nixon supports this?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.18,1:01:04.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可能会 他还不知情\N{\rOriginal text}He probably would. He doesn't know about it
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.56,1:01:10.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}同样 科尔·戴维斯也会永远蒙在鼓里\N{\rOriginal text}in the same way that Cole Davis will never know about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.81,1:01:12.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这应该不是个问题\N{\rOriginal text}And that shouldn't be a problem
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.60,1:01:16.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}毕竟虽然你们越走越近\N{\rOriginal text}considering what else you haven't shared with him
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.94,1:01:18.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但你还是有些事瞒着他\N{\rOriginal text}while you've grown closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.11,1:01:22.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那么帅气的一个人会怎么想...\N{\rOriginal text}I mean, what would a clean-cut guy like that think about...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.57,1:01:23.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你已经说得很清楚了\N{\rOriginal text}You made your point.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.53,1:01:27.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}谁也摆脱不了自己的过往\N{\rOriginal text}No one can outrun their past.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.20,1:01:31.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我可以永远抹除一个人的黑历史\N{\rOriginal text}But I can make it go away. Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.83,1:01:33.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不必再逃亡\N{\rOriginal text}No more running.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.34,1:01:41.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我得需要助理帮忙\N{\rOriginal text}I'm gonna need my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.09,1:01:45.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}当然\N{\rOriginal text}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.30,1:01:49.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们会给你配一个安全特工团队\N{\rOriginal text}And we'll get you a team of secure agents.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.22,1:01:54.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 你手里最厉害 但却没人听说过的导演是谁?\N{\rOriginal text}Now, who's the best director you've got that no one's ever heard of?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.40,1:02:00.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你会喜欢他的\N{\rOriginal text}You're gonna love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.03,1:02:02.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(政府财产 非请莫入)
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.61,1:02:04.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是基地里最偏远的飞机库\N{\rOriginal text}This is the most remote hangar on the base.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.57,1:02:07.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没有我的允许 任何人不得出入\N{\rOriginal text}No one can go in or out without my permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.74,1:02:09.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 任何人? 连科尔都不行?\N{\rOriginal text}Wait, no one? Not even Cole?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.20,1:02:12.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科尔尤其不行\N{\rOriginal text}Especially not Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.58,1:02:18.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}难以置信 凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}Unbelievable, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.09,1:02:20.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你找人强行把我拖上飞机\N{\rOriginal text}You have me... forced onto a plane,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.46,1:02:22.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}把我带到这该死的佛罗里达\N{\rOriginal text}and brought to godforsaken Florida!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.22,1:02:23.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}能松手吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.76,1:02:26.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是美国导演工会成员\N{\rOriginal text}I'm a member of the DGA.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.97,1:02:28.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不能被这样粗暴对待\N{\rOriginal text}I will not be treated this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.31,1:02:31.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要给经纪人打电话 不行\N{\rOriginal text}I am calling my agent. You can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.77,1:02:32.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我这就打给你看\N{\rOriginal text}Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.85,1:02:36.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}记住 我们谈过的 这是安保级别很高的政府项目\N{\rOriginal text}Remember we talked about this. This is a high-security government job.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.19,1:02:39.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我给你的报价翻倍 好吧\N{\rOriginal text}I'm doubling your quote. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.40,1:02:40.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}还有奖金\N{\rOriginal text}With a bonus. Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.57,1:02:45.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 唯一的条件是不能让任何人知道 我们在干什么\N{\rOriginal text}Yes. The only caveat being that no one can ever know what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.41,1:02:47.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这我无法接受 他们会枪毙你\N{\rOriginal text}I cannot accept that. They will shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.37,1:02:49.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}预算是多少?\N{\rOriginal text}What is my budget?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.37,1:02:55.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你花多少钱都行 只要把这里变成月球\N{\rOriginal text}Your budget is whatever it costs to turn this into the moon
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.12,1:02:56.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拍出两个半小时的片子来\N{\rOriginal text}for two-and-a-half hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.29,1:02:58.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}比《宾虚》短\N{\rOriginal text}It's shorter than Ben-Hur.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.02,1:03:16.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我需要在那边摆一台装满汽水的冰箱\N{\rOriginal text}I will need a fridge full of Tab over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.60,1:03:21.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}和一大群不会提问的手下\N{\rOriginal text}And an army of minions who don't ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.20,1:03:35.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉 这些都不是真正的演员\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly, these aren't real actors.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.71,1:03:37.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你只能用他们 这是最好的情况了\N{\rOriginal text}Well, this is the best you're gonna get.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.92,1:03:39.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼尔身高1.8米 谁是1.8米高?\N{\rOriginal text}Neil's 5'11 ". Anybody 5'11"?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.67,1:03:42.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 其他人散了吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. The rest of you are dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.30,1:03:44.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}选吧 等等 你\N{\rOriginal text}Take your pick. Mmm. Hold on. You.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.34,1:03:45.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你来做我的私人助理\N{\rOriginal text}You're gonna be my personal assistant.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.67,1:03:48.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我就叫你约瑟夫 这样有什么事你不会往心里去\N{\rOriginal text}I'll just call you Joseph so you can't take things personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.05,1:03:49.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}随便站一边去吧\N{\rOriginal text}Go stand somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.34,1:03:51.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 能把墨镜都摘了吗?\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Can we take these sunglasses off, please,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.64,1:03:54.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好让我看到你们的眼睛 相信你们的话\N{\rOriginal text}so I can see your eyes and believe your truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.60,1:03:56.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我要每个人来一段独白\N{\rOriginal text}Now, I want each of you to do a monologue.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.39,1:03:59.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}最好是经典桥段 但是老天啊\N{\rOriginal text}Preferably something classical, and by God,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.60,1:04:01.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}千万别给我来七遍《哈姆雷特》\N{\rOriginal text}don't make me watch seven Hamlets.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.23,1:04:03.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你到时候看不见他们的脸 都戴着头盔呢\N{\rOriginal text}You're not gonna see their faces. They're wearing helmets.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.32,1:04:04.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什...\N{\rOriginal text}Wh...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.28,1:04:09.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 那我如何\N{\rOriginal text}All right, how do I convey
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.57,1:04:12.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在不让观众看到人脸的情况下\N{\rOriginal text}the gripping fear of being on the moon for the first time
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.20,1:04:14.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}展示第一次登月那揪心的恐惧?\N{\rOriginal text}if we can't show a human face?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.91,1:04:16.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}表演是一种运动 凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}Acting is a sport, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.16,1:04:18.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}需要能量 身体... 我把设备放哪?\N{\rOriginal text}It is energy, body, bu... Where do I set up?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.67,1:04:20.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}爱德华?\N{\rOriginal text}Edvard? Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.33,1:04:23.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎么进来的? 从门口走进来的\N{\rOriginal text}How did you get in here? I just walked through the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.75,1:04:28.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“此事说出去会害我们被杀” 这句话你哪儿不明白?\N{\rOriginal text}What part of "talking about this is gonna get us killed" do you not understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.68,1:04:31.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而且他是纽约动作最慢的摄影指导 我来选摄影师\N{\rOriginal text}And he's the slowest DP in New York. I pick the cinematographer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.30,1:04:33.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}写在合同里呢 什么? 你没有合同\N{\rOriginal text}It's in my contract. What? You don't have a contract.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.68,1:04:35.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他最棒 所有的摄影指导动作都慢\N{\rOriginal text}He's the best, and all DPs are slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.43,1:04:39.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉 我们最需要的\N{\rOriginal text}What we need to have a serious conversation about, Kelly,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.31,1:04:41.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就是美术指导\N{\rOriginal text}is production design, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.60,1:04:44.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们用什么材料来仿造月球表面?\N{\rOriginal text}What materials are we using to recreate the lunar surface?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.82,1:04:46.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}月球就是块大石头 对吧?\N{\rOriginal text}It's just a big rock, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.78,1:04:56.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我没法这样工作 凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}I can't work like this, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.08,1:05:00.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你是了解我这一点的\N{\rOriginal text}You know this about me. Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.00,1:05:01.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我需要细节\N{\rOriginal text}I need details.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.62,1:05:04.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们需要细节 具体细节\N{\rOriginal text}We need details. Specifics.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.71,1:05:08.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是多尘 多石还是有风? 光源是怎样的?\N{\rOriginal text}Is it dusty, rocky, windy? What is the light source? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.34,1:05:12.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就是太阳咯 大灯 别自作聪明 爱德华\N{\rOriginal text}It's the sun. Big light. Do not smart-mouth me, Edvard.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.30,1:05:16.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}太阳和着陆区的位置关系是怎样的?\N{\rOriginal text}And what is the sun's position in relation to the landing area?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.10,1:05:18.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们要建一个仿制版吗? 我们有计划吗?\N{\rOriginal text}And are we building a replica? Do we have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.18,1:05:21.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们有宇航服吗? 演员穿上宇航服如何行动?\N{\rOriginal text}Do we have suits, and how do people move in those suits?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.73,1:05:24.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}还有 凯莉 太空里到底什么样子?\N{\rOriginal text}And what, Kelly, does space even look like?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.27,1:05:26.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 得躺一下\N{\rOriginal text}You know, I gotta... I gotta lie down.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.27,1:05:28.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我的拖车呢?\N{\rOriginal text}Where is my trailer?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.32,1:05:34.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们得想办法 把那个模拟室里的一切都照搬过来\N{\rOriginal text}We need to find a way to copy everything in that simulation room.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.70,1:05:36.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好的 尽快\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.33,1:05:38.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 我有拖车吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Wait a second. Do I even have a trailer?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.58,1:05:41.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不说话我也知道\N{\rOriginal text}Your silence tells me what I already know.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.54,1:05:43.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你还没想过怎样复刻月球\N{\rOriginal text}You haven't thought about how to recreate the moon,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.58,1:05:46.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎么会想拖车的事? 我觉得我们该找库布里克了\N{\rOriginal text}why would you think about a trailer? I think we should've gotten Kubrick.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.63,1:05:48.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们必须把新的飞船做对了\N{\rOriginal text}We've got to get this new ship right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.50,1:05:50.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿姆斯特朗很生气\N{\rOriginal text}I mean, Armstrong, he was pissed off
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.26,1:05:51.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们不能再惹他了 抱歉\N{\rOriginal text}and we can't have that again. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.38,1:05:54.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}伙计...\N{\rOriginal text}Buddy, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.43,1:05:56.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等... 这些都是敏感材料\N{\rOriginal text}Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa. This is sensitive material.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.47,1:05:58.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}亨利... 不行 你不能待在这里\N{\rOriginal text}Henry. Henry. Uh-uh. You can't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.39,1:06:01.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这些照片是为了企鹅出版社的档案书拍的\N{\rOriginal text}These photos are for the archival book that Penguin is doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.18,1:06:02.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什么书? 对 你没收到备忘录?\N{\rOriginal text}What book? Yeah, didn't you get the memo?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.98,1:06:04.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没有 什么? 你要写前言\N{\rOriginal text}No. What? You're writing the foreword.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.44,1:06:07.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 写前言? 对 是啊\N{\rOriginal text}I... I'm writing the foreword? Yeah, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.27,1:06:08.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我? 没错\N{\rOriginal text}Me? Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.82,1:06:11.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我从没写过前言 编辑想听听你的话\N{\rOriginal text}I've never written a foreword. The editor wants to hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.19,1:06:12.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们都想 他要我写?\N{\rOriginal text}We all do. He wants me to write it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.49,1:06:14.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别这么谦虚好吗? 我们给你拍一张和...\N{\rOriginal text}Don't be so humble, all right? Let's get a photo of you with the...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.82,1:06:16.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}登月舱的合影 我可以写 但...\N{\rOriginal text}with the LEM. I mean, I can do it, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.41,1:06:17.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}说“我们要登月了”\N{\rOriginal text}Say, "we're going to the moon."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.62,1:06:19.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们要登月了 真不错\N{\rOriginal text}We're going to the moon. There you go!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.29,1:06:23.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}奥尔德林和阿姆斯特朗 每一个动作都要练习\N{\rOriginal text}Aldrin and Armstrong will practice every single movement that they make,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.46,1:06:25.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在这里练好几个月\N{\rOriginal text}um, right here for months.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.33,1:06:26.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真了不起 是\N{\rOriginal text}That is incredible. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.71,1:06:28.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这就是月球表面?\N{\rOriginal text}So, this is, like, the surface of the moon?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.96,1:06:30.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 这... 对\N{\rOriginal text}Well, yeah. It's... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.09,1:06:31.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是我们最接近的模拟\N{\rOriginal text}It's our best approximation.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.97,1:06:34.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这看起来就像个肮脏的海滩 我不信 不可能\N{\rOriginal text}This just looks like a dirty beach. I don't believe it. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.38,1:06:36.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是按... 我们得到的沉积物做的 约瑟夫\N{\rOriginal text}It is... It's based off sediment we got. Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.34,1:06:37.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}来自航天局\N{\rOriginal text}It's from NASA...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.26,1:06:40.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 我不相信这就是国家航空航天局\N{\rOriginal text}Wait. I do not believe this is what NASA uses
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.14,1:06:42.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}用来登月的装备 你别告诉我... 不行\N{\rOriginal text}to go to the moon. You cannot tell me... No.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.31,1:06:46.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要你们假装抱着母亲在沙漠里行走\N{\rOriginal text}Want you to walk as if you're carrying your mother across the desert.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.40,1:06:49.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她很脆弱 但也很重\N{\rOriginal text}She's frail but also heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.61,1:06:51.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 嘿\N{\rOriginal text}Oh. Whoa. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.28,1:06:52.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真抱歉 嘿 对不起 不能拍...\N{\rOriginal text}So sorry. Hey. Sorry. Oh, no, no. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.82,1:06:54.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是机密 你不能... 斯图 没事\N{\rOriginal text}This is classified. You're not allow... Stu, we're good.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.61,1:06:56.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是机密 没事 这是为那本书拍的\N{\rOriginal text}Very classified. We're good here. This is for the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.45,1:06:57.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你会听说的\N{\rOriginal text}No, you'll hear about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.57,1:06:58.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要写前言\N{\rOriginal text}I'm doing the foreword,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.49,1:06:59.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你很快会听说的 好吧\N{\rOriginal text}so you'll hear about it soon. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.83,1:07:02.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我这个阿姆斯特朗是个总爱抱怨的烂人 我们得重新选角\N{\rOriginal text}My Armstrong is a whiny, little bitch. We have to recast.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.66,1:07:04.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 我们不重新选角\N{\rOriginal text}No... We're not recasting.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.83,1:07:06.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 那就平庸着拍吧\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Well, mediocre it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.54,1:07:09.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}爱德华 我的太阳呢?\N{\rOriginal text}Edvard! Where is my sun?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.84,1:07:10.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很好\N{\rOriginal text}Nice!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.84,1:07:12.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常好 至少来个倒数啊\N{\rOriginal text}Very nice. A countdown at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.09,1:07:14.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 再开一次\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Try it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.34,1:07:15.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我再开一次 从三倒数\N{\rOriginal text}Gonna try it again. Do a three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.97,1:07:17.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜托 满意吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Come on! Ah! Happy?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.05,1:07:19.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}约瑟夫 给我拿汽水来\N{\rOriginal text}J... Joseph, bring me my Tab.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.35,1:07:21.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你得来找我 因为我眼都瞎了\N{\rOriginal text}You're gonna have to find me 'cause I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.60,1:07:23.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜托 拿个汽水要多久?\N{\rOriginal text}Come on. How long does it take to give someone a Tab?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.73,1:07:25.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我的手就在这里\N{\rOriginal text}My hand's right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.31,1:07:27.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一定会很棒的 你们都该聚过来\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, this will be great. You guys should all come around
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.31,1:07:29.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们来给那本书拍一张 很好吧?\N{\rOriginal text}and we'll do a shot for the book. Great?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.48,1:07:32.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 各位 这么说如何? “我们要登月了”\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, how about this? Everybody, "We're going to the moon!"
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.03,1:07:35.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们要登月了\N{\rOriginal text}We're going to the moon!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.90,1:07:38.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我好像眨眼了 再拍一张?\N{\rOriginal text}My eyes might have been closed. You wanna do one more?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.70,1:07:43.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}最近没看到你\N{\rOriginal text}I haven't seen you around lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.33,1:07:45.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}彼此彼此\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I can say the same thing about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.33,1:07:49.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎么一次就系好了?\N{\rOriginal text}How do you do it on the first try?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.04,1:07:52.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这又不是多复杂的事 好 准备好了吗?\N{\rOriginal text}It's not rocket science. Okay. You good?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.55,1:07:54.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那些问题 我... 是的\N{\rOriginal text}About the questions, I... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.76,1:07:59.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我都看过了 没有关于阿波罗1号的 他们答应过我 好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}I went over them. Nothing about Apollo 1. They promised me. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.51,1:08:02.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你会表现得很好的 明白吗?\N{\rOriginal text}You're gonna be great. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.26,1:08:03.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}去吧\N{\rOriginal text}Mm-hmm. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.51,1:08:04.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 上\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.19,1:08:10.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}戴维斯先生 你是我们口中的“采访困难户”\N{\rOriginal text}Mr. Davis. You are what we call "a tough get."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.10,1:08:11.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哪有 谢谢\N{\rOriginal text}Ha! No. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.19,1:08:14.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们将看到尼尔阿姆斯特朗 和巴兹奥尔德林走上月球表面\N{\rOriginal text}Is there any legal importance to what we'll be watching
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.48,1:08:18.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这有什么法律方面的重要意义吗?\N{\rOriginal text}when Neil Armstrong and Buzz Aldrin walk on the lunar surface?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.11,1:08:22.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们着陆的区域会被视为归美国所有吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Will the area they land on be considered property of the United States?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.16,1:08:25.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们要送一块匾上去 写着“我们为全人类的和平而来”\N{\rOriginal text}We're sending a plaque that says, "We came in peace for all mankind."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.83,1:08:27.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那正是我们的意思\N{\rOriginal text}And that is precisely what we mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.41,1:08:29.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}国家航空航天局还会留下其他什么东西?\N{\rOriginal text}What else will NASA leave behind?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.96,1:08:32.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}足迹 一面美国国旗和12袋粪便\N{\rOriginal text}Footprints, an American flag and 12 bags of feces
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.29,1:08:35.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们跟我说了很多次不要提 但是...\N{\rOriginal text}that I was told many times that I should not bring up, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.25,1:08:37.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们真该早点让他接受采访\N{\rOriginal text}Should've put him in front of a camera sooner.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.22,1:08:38.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你戴着一枚阿波罗胸针\N{\rOriginal text}You wear an Apollo pin.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.93,1:08:41.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的\N{\rOriginal text}I do. Um,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.43,1:08:43.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是阿波罗1号乘组的太太们\N{\rOriginal text}the wives of Apollo 1's men,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.01,1:08:47.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在丈夫们牺牲后送我的\N{\rOriginal text}after we lost them, they gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.10,1:08:50.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在那悲剧的一天 你是发射主管\N{\rOriginal text}You were launch director on that tragic day.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.02,1:08:53.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗1号出了什么故障?\N{\rOriginal text}What went wrong with Apollo 1?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.99,1:08:59.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}用你自己的话说 发生了什么?\N{\rOriginal text}In your own words, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.49,1:09:02.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}帮我回顾一下\N{\rOriginal text}Take me back.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.79,1:09:09.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我来给你列举一些事实\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Here's some facts for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.83,1:09:11.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}《纽约时报》报道\N{\rOriginal text}The New York Times reported
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.00,1:09:13.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那艘飞船曾有两万份安全事件报告\N{\rOriginal text}there were 20,000 safety reports filed about that ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.71,1:09:17.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}实在太多 以至于加斯·格里森 用一个柠檬表示自己的不满\N{\rOriginal text}So many, that Gus Grissom hung a lemon outside it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.97,1:09:22.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 乘组 待确认 位置\N{\rOriginal text}All right, crew. To be confirmed. Location.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.97,1:09:23.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}着火了\N{\rOriginal text}Flame!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.97,1:09:26.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}驾驶舱里失火了\N{\rOriginal text}We've got a fire in the cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.06,1:09:26.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}快出去\N{\rOriginal text}Let's get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.97,1:09:29.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}戴维斯先生 你读过那些报告吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Mr. Davis? Did you read those reports?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.98,1:09:32.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}发射台主管 快进去救他们\N{\rOriginal text}Pad leader, get in there and help 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.65,1:09:34.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}发射台主管 盯着C3\N{\rOriginal text}Pad leader, stay on C3.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.61,1:09:43.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}戴维斯先生 你读过那些报告吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Mr. Davis? Did you read those reports?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.32,1:09:49.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你读过那些报告吗? 我当然读过那些报告\N{\rOriginal text}Did you read those reports? Of course I read the reports.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.95,1:09:51.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每一份都读过\N{\rOriginal text}I read every single one of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.16,1:09:55.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}独立供电测试期间 氧气压力过高的同时遇到了线路故障\N{\rOriginal text}Overpressured oxygen and a bad wire on a "plugs-out" test.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.17,1:10:00.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我本该查出一切问题的 我看漏了 辜负了他们\N{\rOriginal text}I was supposed to catch everything, and I missed it. And I failed them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.21,1:10:03.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我余生中的每一天都会为此感到愧疚\N{\rOriginal text}And I will live with that every single day for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.05,1:10:05.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人渣 这是你想引述的原话吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Is that the quote that you were looking for, you piece of shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.68,1:10:08.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}让我跟你的老板通话 立刻 马上\N{\rOriginal text}Get me on the phone with your boss. Now. Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.39,1:10:12.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 你干什么? 采访还有20分钟\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, uh, wait. W-What are you doing? We have another 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.39,1:10:13.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}去死吧\N{\rOriginal text}Go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.48,1:10:16.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别生我的气 害死三个宇航员的人不是我\N{\rOriginal text}Don't be angry with me. I'm not the reason three astronauts are dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.90,1:10:22.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你再提一句那些宇航员试试 嘿... 别冲动\N{\rOriginal text}Say one more thing about the astronauts. Hey, hey, hey! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.99,1:10:24.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}放开我 你再说一句试试\N{\rOriginal text}Get off me. Let me hear you say one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.91,1:10:26.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你再提他们一句试试\N{\rOriginal text}Let me hear you say one more thing about them!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.70,1:10:28.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不认识他们 你不准再提他们\N{\rOriginal text}You don't know those men! You don't talk about those men!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.87,1:10:30.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}放开我 放开\N{\rOriginal text}Get off me! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.66,1:10:31.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}放开\N{\rOriginal text}Get off!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.25,1:10:33.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}听懂了吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.30,1:10:43.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我跟制作人们谈过了 他们同意不播出这段采访\N{\rOriginal text}So, I spoke to the producers, and they've agreed to seal the film
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.47,1:10:47.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}条件是阿姆斯特朗着陆后 给他们独家采访\N{\rOriginal text}if we give them the exclusive with Armstrong after he lands.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.35,1:10:54.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不过我们失去了赫奇斯的支持 他要投反对票了\N{\rOriginal text}We lost Hedges though. He's voting no.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.48,1:10:59.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你说过他们不会问的 是的 他们撒谎了\N{\rOriginal text}You said they wouldn't ask about it. Yeah. Well... they lied.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.94,1:11:01.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人们有时是会撒谎的 科尔\N{\rOriginal text}You know, people do that sometimes, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.57,1:11:03.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你也许可以说点假话 那也算为自己\N{\rOriginal text}You could have done yourself and this program a favor
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.57,1:11:05.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}和这登月计划帮了个忙 对吗?\N{\rOriginal text}and maybe tried it yourself. Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.61,1:11:07.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}责怪国家航空航天局\N{\rOriginal text}Blame NASA.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.45,1:11:08.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}责怪这个体系\N{\rOriginal text}Blame the system.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.45,1:11:12.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}事关价值五亿美元的资金啊\N{\rOriginal text}I mean, there was half a billion dollars worth of funding on the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.12,1:11:14.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}撒谎对你来说一定轻而易举吧 毕竟你总在撒谎\N{\rOriginal text}Lying must be so easy for you when you do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.46,1:11:15.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}撒谎总是一个可选项\N{\rOriginal text}It's just always an option.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.67,1:11:18.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你该试试说真话 你装什么清高呢?\N{\rOriginal text}What you should try is the truth. What is this sanctimonious bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.21,1:11:20.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我永远不会就那些人或那一天的事撒谎\N{\rOriginal text}I'm never going to lie about those men or that day.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.88,1:11:22.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你明白吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.96,1:11:24.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}随便你怎么看我\N{\rOriginal text}You think what you want about me,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.63,1:11:28.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但因为不冷静 而让全人类登月梦破碎的人不是我\N{\rOriginal text}but I didn't cost the world a dream because I lost my goddamn cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.33,1:12:02.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是34号发射场 发生阿波罗1号悲剧的地方\N{\rOriginal text}This is Launch Complex 34, where the Apollo 1 tragedy occurred.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.50,1:12:05.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是牺牲英雄的纪念碑\N{\rOriginal text}This is a tribute to our fallen heroes,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.21,1:12:08.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这些勇敢的人为我们的成功铺平了道路\N{\rOriginal text}the brave men who paved the road to our success.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.84,1:12:12.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请大家为他们默哀片刻\N{\rOriginal text}Please, let's take a moment of silence for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.86,1:12:25.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}爱德华 真令人称奇\N{\rOriginal text}Edvard, that looks incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.19,1:12:27.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我完全看不到线缆 你怎么做到的?\N{\rOriginal text}I can't see the wires at all. How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.03,1:12:29.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只是用了一块遮光板 很简单\N{\rOriginal text}I just put a flag. It's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.03,1:12:29.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}老办法了\N{\rOriginal text}Old school. Huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.95,1:12:32.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不行 从头再来\N{\rOriginal text}No. Again. From the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.45,1:12:35.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这次多加一些跳跃\N{\rOriginal text}And maybe let's get some more bounce this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.12,1:12:36.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们可是在月球上啊\N{\rOriginal text}You are on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.75,1:12:38.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.42,1:12:46.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 我看不下去了 今天不行\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, my God. I-I can't. I can't with this day.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.88,1:12:50.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 好 坚持住 约瑟夫 失火了\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, dear. Uh... Okay, hold on. Joseph, there's a fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.80,1:12:51.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我来\N{\rOriginal text}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.60,1:12:54.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别忘记四步口诀\N{\rOriginal text}Don't forget to PASS.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.90,1:13:03.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 能放他们下来吗? 算了 挂着吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Can you bring them down? Actually, leave them up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.23,1:13:05.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}让他们反思一下自己都干了什么\N{\rOriginal text}Let them think about what they did.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.32,1:13:09.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我放弃了 我去吃午饭\N{\rOriginal text}I give up. I'm taking lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.24,1:13:16.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们明白自己干了什么吗? 你们让她提早去吃午饭了\N{\rOriginal text}You see what you did? You made her take lunch early.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.37,1:13:18.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这都怪你们\N{\rOriginal text}That's on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.01,1:13:32.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我跟你赌5美元 你不擅长道歉\N{\rOriginal text}I'll bet you $5 you're bad at apologies.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.47,1:13:33.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我到处找你\N{\rOriginal text}I've been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.76,1:13:35.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你欠我5块 我有个想法\N{\rOriginal text}You owe me five bucks. I got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.35,1:13:36.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什么?\N{\rOriginal text}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.43,1:13:38.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}来 去路易斯安那州的路上告诉你\N{\rOriginal text}Come on. I'll tell you on the way to Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.89,1:13:41.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 你想尝试获得范宁的投票?\N{\rOriginal text}No. You wanna take a shot at Vanning?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.98,1:13:44.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我给咱们弄到了晚餐邀请 就是今晚 走吧\N{\rOriginal text}I got us a dinner invite, for tonight. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.94,1:13:46.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}今晚? 我们不可能赶得上 有800公里呢\N{\rOriginal text}Tonight? We're never gonna make it. It's 500 miles away.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.98,1:13:49.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们能赶上 来 你得相信我\N{\rOriginal text}We're gonna make it. Come on. You gotta trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.94,1:13:50.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 不\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, wait. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.99,1:13:52.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不行... 什么叫“不行”?\N{\rOriginal text}No, no, no. What do you mean, "no"?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.32,1:13:54.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们不能... 有其他... 我们可以... 你想不想要范宁支持?\N{\rOriginal text}We don't... There's other... We could... Do you want Vanning or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.70,1:13:56.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不... 来 我们走\N{\rOriginal text}Ugh. No. I don't... Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.66,1:13:58.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我觉得我们可以乘民航 如果我们出发...\N{\rOriginal text}I think we could just take a commercial flight. If we left...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.83,1:14:00.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不行 现在没有民航航班\N{\rOriginal text}Nope. No commercial flights are flying right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.75,1:14:02.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}来 跳上来\N{\rOriginal text}Come on. Just hop on in.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.42,1:14:05.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就是这样 你只管上来就行 你可以跳上来的 你行的\N{\rOriginal text}This is it. This is all you gotta do. You can hop up, you can get in.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.13,1:14:06.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}脚踩那里 好吧 拿着我的鞋\N{\rOriginal text}Put your foot there. Okay, well, take these.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.92,1:14:08.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}听着 我们得走了 好\N{\rOriginal text}Look, we gotta go. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.38,1:14:09.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等...\N{\rOriginal text}Hold on. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.13,1:14:13.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}完美\N{\rOriginal text}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.26,1:14:15.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 没问题\N{\rOriginal text}Hold on. We're good.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.90,1:14:27.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}风景不错吧?\N{\rOriginal text}You enjoying the view?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.27,1:14:28.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 太美了\N{\rOriginal text}Wow! It's stunning!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.61,1:14:31.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我打赌你闭着眼呢\N{\rOriginal text}I bet your eyes are closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.24,1:14:33.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没有\N{\rOriginal text}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.17,1:14:46.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我猜你还会些其他南方口音\N{\rOriginal text}So, I'm betting you have some other Southern accents
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.96,1:14:48.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}毕竟你“多才多艺” 会路易斯安那的吗?\N{\rOriginal text}in that bag of tricks of yours. Can you do Louisiana?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.92,1:14:50.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}会 新奥尔良还是巴吞鲁日?\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. New Orleans or Baton Rouge?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.46,1:14:52.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}用他老婆家乡的 好\N{\rOriginal text}Wherever his wife's from. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.68,1:14:56.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科尔·戴维斯\N{\rOriginal text}Cole Davis.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.01,1:14:57.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你一定是凯莉·琼斯小姐\N{\rOriginal text}And you must be Miss Kelly Jones.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.89,1:14:59.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}两位请进\N{\rOriginal text}Please come in, y'all. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.31,1:15:00.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常感谢你们邀请我们吃晚餐\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you so much for having us for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.89,1:15:04.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好... 我听说你是纽约城里人\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, now... now, I was told you were a New York City type.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.48,1:15:06.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 不是 我只是在那里工作 我是路易斯安那人\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, God, no. I just work there. I'm from Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.94,1:15:08.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}土生土长的 也会落叶归根\N{\rOriginal text}Born and raised and, one day, buried.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.31,1:15:11.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我老家在弗吉尼亚 不会吧? 我们是亲人啊\N{\rOriginal text}I'm from Virginia. No? We're family.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.07,1:15:14.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}特克·斯里特尔总说 弗吉尼亚是得克萨斯的母亲\N{\rOriginal text}You know, Tex Ritter always said Virginia was the mother of Texas.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.65,1:15:17.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们一直不知道父亲是谁 总怀疑是路易斯安那\N{\rOriginal text}Well, we never knew who the father was. We always suspected it was Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.91,1:15:19.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我妈可喜欢这个笑话了\N{\rOriginal text}Oh! Huh? My mother loves that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.91,1:15:22.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是她想出来的 太有意思了\N{\rOriginal text}She was the one that came up with it. Oh, just so colorful.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.08,1:15:25.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你真有趣 你家可真漂亮\N{\rOriginal text}You're fun. This is a beautiful home.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.33,1:15:31.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}参议员 竞选活动怎么样?\N{\rOriginal text}So, h-how is the campaign going, Senator?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.71,1:15:35.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}说实话 政治更像是我的一项爱好\N{\rOriginal text}Truth be told, politics is more of a hobby to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.09,1:15:40.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}服事基督才是我的全职工作\N{\rOriginal text}Serving Christ, that's my full-time job.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.93,1:15:44.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}现在美国正有一场针对宗教的战争\N{\rOriginal text}You know, there's a war on religion in this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.48,1:15:47.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有人说要怪科学\N{\rOriginal text}And some say science is to blame.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.44,1:15:50.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是科学让我们今天齐聚一堂\N{\rOriginal text}Well, science is what brought us to this table.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.57,1:15:53.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你从阿波罗1号的事上学到了\N{\rOriginal text}You learned a little lesson on the provocation of pride
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.19,1:15:55.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}关于骄傲的一课 科尔 不是吗?\N{\rOriginal text}on Apollo 1, now, didn't you, Cole?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.95,1:16:01.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}其实科学让我离上帝更近了 先生\N{\rOriginal text}Science has actually brought me closer to God, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.66,1:16:05.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}上帝用了六天创造了我们所知的一切\N{\rOriginal text}Took the Lord six days to put forth everything that we know as creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.54,1:16:07.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}第六天 他把这些交给我们管理\N{\rOriginal text}And on that sixth day he gave us dominion over it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.92,1:16:10.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我个人认为这是一种责任\N{\rOriginal text}And, personally, I take that as a responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.46,1:16:15.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你听起来很虔诚\N{\rOriginal text}You sound like a man who knows his way to church.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.42,1:16:18.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我觉得最能体现虔诚的方法\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I can't think of a greater act of faith
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.84,1:16:20.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫过于追逐星辰\N{\rOriginal text}than pursuing the stars.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.51,1:16:25.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“诸天述说上帝的荣耀 穹苍传扬他的作为”\N{\rOriginal text}"The heavens declare the glory of God. And the firmament shows us his handiwork."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.52,1:16:29.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是乔琳娜最喜欢的诗篇句子之一\N{\rOriginal text}That's one of Jolene's favorite Psalms.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.15,1:16:31.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是这样 等我们的人从太空归来\N{\rOriginal text}You see, our men, when they come back from space,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.69,1:16:34.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们对上帝的信仰会更多 不会减少\N{\rOriginal text}they believe more in God, not less.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.49,1:16:37.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我们登月时\N{\rOriginal text}But when we land on the moon,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.49,1:16:43.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}多亏了这位琼斯小姐 全球都能看到\N{\rOriginal text}and thanks to Miss Jones here, the world watches us do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.16,1:16:47.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我希望世界各地的人都能感受到 那种圣神的存在\N{\rOriginal text}And it's my hope that people everywhere feel the presence of that divine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.83,1:16:52.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧\N{\rOriginal text}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.63,1:16:58.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你的话确实得让我好好想想 小伙子\N{\rOriginal text}you've, uh, certainly given me a lot to think about, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.64,1:17:09.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你这推销还真有说服力啊\N{\rOriginal text}You really sold the hell out of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.85,1:17:11.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我没在推销\N{\rOriginal text}I wasn't selling.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.98,1:17:16.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}郑重声明 做真实的自己也能赢得人心\N{\rOriginal text}For the record, you can win people over just by being who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.86,1:17:24.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们现在不赶时间了 所以不必飞回去\N{\rOriginal text}You know, we're not in a rush, so we don't really have to fly home.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.87,1:17:26.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那可不算飞\N{\rOriginal text}Ooh. That wasn't flying.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.09,1:17:39.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜托 睁开眼睛\N{\rOriginal text}Come on. Open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.48,1:17:51.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}相信我吗?\N{\rOriginal text}You trust me?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.90,1:17:55.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}坐稳了\N{\rOriginal text}Hold tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.70,1:18:07.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}现在才是最好玩的 滑下来就行\N{\rOriginal text}Now, this is the fun part. Just slide off.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.37,1:18:13.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}完美\N{\rOriginal text}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.75,1:19:05.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我过去对国家航空航天局的计划 有过诸多意见不一致的地方\N{\rOriginal text}I've had my disagreements with the NASA program in the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.43,1:19:09.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但经过深思熟虑和反复祈祷后\N{\rOriginal text}But after a great deal of thought, and prayer,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.97,1:19:12.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我决定投赞成票\N{\rOriginal text}I've decided to vote yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.48,1:19:17.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好样的\N{\rOriginal text}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.11,1:19:21.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我有样东西 你一定得看看\N{\rOriginal text}I have something that you need to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.49,1:19:23.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什么... 跟我来\N{\rOriginal text}What... Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.57,1:19:25.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我之前不知道结果会如何\N{\rOriginal text}Whoo! I didn't know which way it was gonna go,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.91,1:19:28.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为你根本看不透政客\N{\rOriginal text}'cause you can't tell with these guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.12,1:19:31.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我之前向来不喜欢这家伙\N{\rOriginal text}I never liked that guy before, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.08,1:19:33.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我现在喜欢他了\N{\rOriginal text}I like him now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.71,1:19:34.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}太好了\N{\rOriginal text}All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.96,1:19:37.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这里好黑啊 你... 快到了\N{\rOriginal text}It's so dark in here. You... Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.13,1:19:39.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我有点害怕 好了 就在这里\N{\rOriginal text}I'm a little scared. Yeah, it's right around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.84,1:19:41.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(对你的感谢有如登月往返)
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.71,1:19:44.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们想对你表达谢意\N{\rOriginal text}We wanted to show you our appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.51,1:19:47.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 这也太隆重了 谢谢\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, my gosh. This is too much. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.89,1:19:49.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不敢相信 都是沃尔特的功劳\N{\rOriginal text}I can't believe it. It was all Walter.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.93,1:19:51.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沃尔特? 我知道这都是你操办的 对吧?\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, Walter? I know that you did all of this, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.97,1:19:53.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}出了点力而已 是 我知道是你\N{\rOriginal text}A little. That's all. Yeah, I know you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.89,1:19:55.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大家都帮忙了 还不错吧?\N{\rOriginal text}They all helped. Not too bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.49,1:20:13.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}趁我还没忘 给\N{\rOriginal text}Before I forget. Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.95,1:20:16.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这上面列出了 登月后你迈出第一步时可以说的话\N{\rOriginal text}It's a list of things for you to say when you take your first step.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.50,1:20:19.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 知道所有人都在问你 就是想给你些点子\N{\rOriginal text}I... I know everybody's asking you. I thought I'd give you some options.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.25,1:20:21.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我本来想说\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I was just gonna say,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.59,1:20:23.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“看这些酷酷的石头”之类的话\N{\rOriginal text}"Look at all those cool rocks," or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.96,1:20:26.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我能搞定的 凯莉 好\N{\rOriginal text}I got this one, Kelly. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.34,1:20:28.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不过谢谢你\N{\rOriginal text}And thank you, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.55,1:20:32.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真心的 谢谢... 你所做的一切\N{\rOriginal text}And I mean it. For, uh... For everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.14,1:20:38.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我觉得没有人比科尔·戴维斯 更在乎这个计划\N{\rOriginal text}You know, I don't think anyone cares about this program more than Cole Davis.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.77,1:20:43.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很高兴看见他有其他在乎的东西了\N{\rOriginal text}It's nice to see he's found something else to care about.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.63,1:21:06.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我知道我不是宇航员 但我能请你跳一支舞吗?\N{\rOriginal text}I know I'm no, uh, astronaut, but can I steal you for a dance?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.55,1:21:09.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可以 可以? 来\N{\rOriginal text}Yes. Yes. Yeah? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.64,1:21:22.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你在数着日子 等待回到曼哈顿的那一天吗?\N{\rOriginal text}So, you just counting down the days until you, uh, can get back to Manhattan?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.69,1:21:23.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}并没有\N{\rOriginal text}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.98,1:21:25.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很好\N{\rOriginal text}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.00,1:21:48.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}往上... 很好 好了 把灯搬过来\N{\rOriginal text}Up, up, up. Perfect. Right, now, move the light in.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.30,1:21:50.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 继续 别害羞\N{\rOriginal text}All right, keep going. Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.34,1:21:53.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}继续...\N{\rOriginal text}Keep going. Keep going. Keep going. Keep going. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.89,1:21:57.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}充分利用 很好\N{\rOriginal text}Milk it. Good. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.68,1:22:00.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}女士们 觉得如何?\N{\rOriginal text}Ladies, what do we think?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.94,1:22:03.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}兰斯 太惊人了 很棒\N{\rOriginal text}Lance, it's incredible. It's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.40,1:22:07.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我觉得还需要再来点尘土和更好的演员\N{\rOriginal text}I think it needs a little more dust and better actors,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.28,1:22:09.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我的要求被拒了\N{\rOriginal text}but I lost that battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.94,1:22:10.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我也就不纠结了\N{\rOriginal text}I will let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.03,1:22:14.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}停 好\N{\rOriginal text}And, stop. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.99,1:22:16.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们有太阳了\N{\rOriginal text}We've got our sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.91,1:22:19.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我总是配合你编造的那些谎言\N{\rOriginal text}I always went along with every web you spun
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.04,1:22:23.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}要么是因为它们很有趣 要么我们是在骗坏人\N{\rOriginal text}because it was fun or, like, we were pulling one over on the bad guys,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.08,1:22:25.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但这次的感觉...\N{\rOriginal text}but this feels...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.13,1:22:26.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我知道\N{\rOriginal text}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.00,1:22:29.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就快完工了\N{\rOriginal text}We're almost done.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.47,1:22:35.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是我送你的\N{\rOriginal text}This is from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.76,1:22:37.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}发射日礼物\N{\rOriginal text}It is for launch day.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.01,1:22:40.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}答应我 到时候再拆\N{\rOriginal text}Promise you will wait until then.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.73,1:22:42.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我答应 好\N{\rOriginal text}I promise. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.77,1:22:46.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}记住 你们不是怪兽\N{\rOriginal text}Remember, you're not monsters.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.19,1:22:49.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}会跳那么高吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Are they gonna be that high?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.44,1:22:52.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只需要让他们的跳跃距离\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, I just need to give them any length
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.70,1:22:55.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}看起来像在月球上即可 但谢谢你的意见\N{\rOriginal text}that looks like they're on the moon. But thank you for the note.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.70,1:22:57.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}巴兹 动作幅度小一点\N{\rOriginal text}Buzz, take it down some.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.83,1:22:59.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿姆斯特朗 不要看我寻求肯定\N{\rOriginal text}And, Armstrong, stop looking at me for approval.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.99,1:23:03.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}专心演好身处月球 把我当空气 他排练得很开心...\N{\rOriginal text}Just be on the moon. I'm not here. He's having fun. He's having fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.67,1:23:06.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他总是和我四目相交 别暗送秋波了 专心演身处月球\N{\rOriginal text}He keeps locking eyes with me. Stop flirting and be on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.80,1:23:18.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}昨天的科幻小说成为了今天的现实\N{\rOriginal text}Yesterday's science fiction is today's fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.85,1:23:20.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}方法虽然不同\N{\rOriginal text}The methods are different,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.26,1:23:22.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但重要的是明天一早\N{\rOriginal text}but the important thing is that tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.81,1:23:25.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人类将飞向月球\N{\rOriginal text}man will lift off toward the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.82,1:23:40.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}晚上好 我是沃尔特·克朗凯特\N{\rOriginal text}Good evening. I'm Walter Cronkite.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.24,1:23:44.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在人类首次登月之旅的前夕\N{\rOriginal text}And on this eve of man's first flight toward a landing on the moon,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.25,1:23:46.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所有的准备工作都很顺利\N{\rOriginal text}all preparations go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.79,1:23:48.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天气预报状况良好\N{\rOriginal text}The weather prediction,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.21,1:23:51.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}还有宇航员们的帮助 尼尔 阿姆...\N{\rOriginal text}along with the health of astronauts, Neil Arm...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.20,1:24:21.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎么了?\N{\rOriginal text}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.75,1:24:34.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你很会伤人心啊\N{\rOriginal text}Well, you know how to hurt a fella.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.21,1:24:36.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}礼貌性的电话都不打一个?\N{\rOriginal text}No courtesy call?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.55,1:24:38.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我没有你的电话号码\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I don't have your number.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.26,1:24:39.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你逃跑了\N{\rOriginal text}You ran.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.93,1:24:42.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是你最擅长的事\N{\rOriginal text}That's what you do best.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.35,1:24:46.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你这个备用版本的登月是个错误 我原本就不该参与\N{\rOriginal text}Your alternate version is wrong. I never should've been a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.10,1:24:47.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不干了\N{\rOriginal text}I quit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.98,1:24:48.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}坐\N{\rOriginal text}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.70,1:24:59.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}今天你要扮演谁呢?\N{\rOriginal text}So, who are we gonna be today?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.66,1:25:01.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我来看看\N{\rOriginal text}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.74,1:25:03.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(目的地 希思罗机场)
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.08,1:25:06.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}海伦·帕克\N{\rOriginal text}Ooh, Helen Parker.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.91,1:25:09.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我打赌 你的英国口音一定很纯正\N{\rOriginal text}I bet you do a killer British accent.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.25,1:25:13.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你想一走了之 去当海伦? 请便\N{\rOriginal text}You wanna take off and be Helen? Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.63,1:25:18.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}海伦不必提心吊胆地生活\N{\rOriginal text}Helen doesn't have to look over her shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.01,1:25:20.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没有人会来找你的\N{\rOriginal text}No one is coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.30,1:25:23.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}除非呢?\N{\rOriginal text}Unless?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.30,1:25:28.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}除非你向任何人透露 阿尔忒弥斯计划真实存在\N{\rOriginal text}Unless you ever tell anyone that Project Artemis was real,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.14,1:25:31.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}登月是虚假拍摄的\N{\rOriginal text}and the moon landing was fake.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.06,1:25:34.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}说到这个 计划有变\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, on that score, change of plans.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.24,1:25:39.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们会播出备用版本的登月\N{\rOriginal text}we're going to air the alternate version.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.61,1:25:40.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}无论如何都播\N{\rOriginal text}No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.74,1:25:42.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们从来没打算播出真实的登月\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, you were never gonna broadcast the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.91,1:25:44.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这不光是登月竞赛\N{\rOriginal text}This isn't just a race for the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.91,1:25:50.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而是哪一种意识形态说了算的竞赛\N{\rOriginal text}It is a race for which ideology gets to run things.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.92,1:25:55.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我让一个手下改装了登月舱摄像机 让它只传回声音\N{\rOriginal text}I got one of my men to rig the LEM camera so that it just beams back audio.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.38,1:26:00.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们会把他们的声音同步到你的假舞台上\N{\rOriginal text}We're gonna sync with their sound and, uh, use your fake stage broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.68,1:26:02.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}从头到尾播出\N{\rOriginal text}start to finish.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.09,1:26:07.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}让我第一个代表美国感谢你\N{\rOriginal text}Let me be the first to thank you on behalf of America.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.23,1:26:15.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 别难过 人人都能得到想要的结果\N{\rOriginal text}Come on, don't feel bad. Everybody gets what they want.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.23,1:26:19.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你可以展开新生活 不必再逃避过往\N{\rOriginal text}You get a new life with no past to run from.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.78,1:26:25.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}全世界也不必在共产主义的月光下入眠\N{\rOriginal text}And the world doesn't have to sleep under a communist moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.49,1:26:30.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 巴拿马在召唤\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Panama beckons.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.71,1:26:35.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你最好快点 要赶不上飞机了 海伦\N{\rOriginal text}You better hurry. You're going to... miss your flight, Helen.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.13,1:26:42.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是为阿波罗号太空飞船上宇航员\N{\rOriginal text}This is a typical meal served to astronauts
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.26,1:26:44.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}提供的典型餐点\N{\rOriginal text}aboard Apollo space flights.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.14,1:26:46.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}燕麦片 吐司\N{\rOriginal text}Oatmeal, toast,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.47,1:26:51.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}和一个特制的零重力饮品袋 装的是能量早餐饮品“菓珍”\N{\rOriginal text}and a special zero-gravity pouch. Tang, the energy breakfast drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.27,1:26:53.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}其维生素C含量超过橙汁\N{\rOriginal text}And more vitamin C than orange juice.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.31,1:26:58.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}能量菓珍 太空人和地球家庭的选择\N{\rOriginal text}Energy Tang, for spacemen and Earth families.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.27,1:27:02.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哥伦比亚广播公司呈献 《月球上的人》\N{\rOriginal text}CBS News presents Man On the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.91,1:27:06.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}讲述阿波罗11号的史诗之旅\N{\rOriginal text}The epic journey of Apollo 11
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.16,1:27:09.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就在这历史性事件的前夕\N{\rOriginal text}on the eve of that historic event.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.08,1:27:12.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}本节目由西部电气赞助\N{\rOriginal text}Sponsored by Western Electric,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.71,1:27:15.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}西部电气 贝尔系统的制造和供应单位\N{\rOriginal text}manufacturing and supply unit of the Bell System.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.71,1:27:19.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}本节目由国际纸业赞助 好主意在这里继续...\N{\rOriginal text}And by the International Paper Company, where good ideas roll on...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.30,1:27:25.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(阿波罗计划中的人们)
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.78,1:28:31.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(假日酒店 祝阿波罗11号马到成功)
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.87,1:28:36.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(私人活动 宇航员妻子的早午餐会)
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.72,1:28:49.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎么来了?\N{\rOriginal text}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.31,1:28:54.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我得给你看一样东西\N{\rOriginal text}I need to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.31,1:28:59.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这本来是个应急计划\N{\rOriginal text}It was supposed to be a contingency plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.77,1:29:02.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他是这样说服我的 就是个保险措施\N{\rOriginal text}That's how he sold it. It was an insurance policy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.27,1:29:03.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}以防我们失败\N{\rOriginal text}In case we failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.07,1:29:07.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}知道了也好\N{\rOriginal text}It's good to know...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.70,1:29:09.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你从来没相信过我们\N{\rOriginal text}that you never believed in us.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.91,1:29:10.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我知道你很难过\N{\rOriginal text}I know you're upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.99,1:29:12.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我理解 你理解什么?\N{\rOriginal text}I understand... Oh, what do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.74,1:29:14.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请告诉我你理解什么\N{\rOriginal text}Please tell me what you understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.74,1:29:16.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为你对真相一点都不理解\N{\rOriginal text}'Cause you don't understand shit about truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.62,1:29:18.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果你伪造这次任务...\N{\rOriginal text}If you fake this mission... If you fake this mission,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.67,1:29:22.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那我们之前做出的每一次牺牲全都白费了\N{\rOriginal text}every single thing that we have sacrificed will have been for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.17,1:29:25.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我知道我搞砸了 我知道\N{\rOriginal text}I know I messed up. I know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.55,1:29:28.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但你心里清楚 如果没有我 你们根本走不到今天\N{\rOriginal text}But you know you couldn't have made it to this day without me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.84,1:29:31.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我昨晚大可一走了之 但我没有\N{\rOriginal text}I could've walked away last night, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.34,1:29:35.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我回来是为了弥补这个错误\N{\rOriginal text}I came back to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.18,1:29:38.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}弥补什么?\N{\rOriginal text}Fix what?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.39,1:29:41.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫切断了登月舱的画面 如果我们不一起修好它\N{\rOriginal text}Moe cut the LEM camera, and if we don't fix this together
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.94,1:29:44.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那全世界看到的将会是这个版本\N{\rOriginal text}then this is gonna be the version that the world sees.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.82,1:29:50.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这不是应急计划\N{\rOriginal text}It's not a contingency.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.95,1:29:56.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 你总能让我别无选择\N{\rOriginal text}God, you're so good at leaving me no options.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.54,1:30:03.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 我们去修好它\N{\rOriginal text}Fine, let's fix it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.88,1:30:07.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但等这事结束 我再也不想看到你\N{\rOriginal text}But when this is over, I never wanna see your face again.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.77,1:30:24.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}为理查德·尼克松做事就是这种下场\N{\rOriginal text}This is what happens when you work for Richard Nixon.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.65,1:30:28.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我看了你的素描本 露比\N{\rOriginal text}I got your book, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.53,1:30:30.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你提早拆开了\N{\rOriginal text}You opened it early.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.32,1:30:32.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拆得正是时候\N{\rOriginal text}It came at just the right time.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.25,1:30:43.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}适合发射的大气层\N{\rOriginal text}Proper atmosphere for launch
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.50,1:30:47.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是氧气和氮气的混合物\N{\rOriginal text}which is a combination of oxygen and nitrogen.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.09,1:30:50.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}60%的氧气和40%氮气的大气层\N{\rOriginal text}Sixty percent oxygen and 40% nitrogen atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.92,1:30:53.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}当然 宇航员们呼吸的是\N{\rOriginal text}Of course, the astronauts themselves are breathing pure oxygen
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.80,1:30:55.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}太空服提供的纯氧\N{\rOriginal text}through their space suits.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.14,1:30:59.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很快将进行另一次关键测试\N{\rOriginal text}Coming up shortly will be another key test
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.35,1:31:02.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}届时发射组...\N{\rOriginal text}in which both the, uh, launch crew for the...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.06,1:31:04.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}发射载具组员和飞船乘组\N{\rOriginal text}the launch vehicle crew and the spacecraft team,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.69,1:31:08.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}会和指挥官尼尔·阿姆斯特朗一起\N{\rOriginal text}uh, combine together with the commander, Neil Armstrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.52,1:31:11.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}彻查紧急情况检测系统\N{\rOriginal text}to make a thorough check of the Emergency Detection System.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.36,1:31:12.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这就是该系统...\N{\rOriginal text}This is the system...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.49,1:31:15.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们正在卡纳维拉尔角直播 这创造历史的一天天气晴好\N{\rOriginal text}We're live from the Cape, where it's a beautiful day to make history.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.32,1:31:17.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们将在这里为大家直播发射的部分\N{\rOriginal text}We'll be handling the launch portion of the broadcast from here,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.83,1:31:19.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们在休斯敦的同行\N{\rOriginal text}and our counterparts in Houston
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.45,1:31:21.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}将报道任务控制中心引导的\N{\rOriginal text}will be covering Apollo 11's historic flight,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.75,1:31:23.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗11号历史性的航程\N{\rOriginal text}guided by Mission Control.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.55,1:31:31.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}各位\N{\rOriginal text}Guys!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.59,1:31:33.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}坏了\N{\rOriginal text}It's busted.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.93,1:31:35.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}摄像机的视频前置放大器\N{\rOriginal text}The camera's video preamplifier.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.34,1:31:36.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}坏掉了 好吧 你能修好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}It's destroyed. Okay, can you fix that?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.89,1:31:38.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我也许能从电视上拆一个改装 但...\N{\rOriginal text}I could maybe repurpose a part from a TV, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.72,1:31:40.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好啊 这里有很多电视\N{\rOriginal text}Well, that's fine. There's plenty of TVs around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.64,1:31:42.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}航天局的电视都太老旧了\N{\rOriginal text}NASA's TVs... They are all too old.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.23,1:31:44.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要一台全新的晶体管彩色电视\N{\rOriginal text}I mean a brand-new solid-state color TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.94,1:31:46.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你多快能弄到一台?\N{\rOriginal text}Well, how fast can you get one?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.06,1:31:48.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你送我去电器商店最快要多久?\N{\rOriginal text}How fast can you get me to an electronics store?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.69,1:31:50.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我? 现在佛罗里达交通空前拥堵\N{\rOriginal text}Me? In the worst traffic in Florida history.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.69,1:31:51.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}走不开 得给大家做准备\N{\rOriginal text}I can't. I have to prep the guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.94,1:31:53.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}把钥匙给我\N{\rOriginal text}Give me the keys.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.78,1:31:55.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 我来拖延\N{\rOriginal text}Fine, I'll stall.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.95,1:31:57.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}快点 去吧...\N{\rOriginal text}Hurry. Go, go, go, go, go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.62,1:32:05.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所有酒店全部爆满\N{\rOriginal text}Hotels are at capacity.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.16,1:32:07.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}肯尼迪航天中心人满为患\N{\rOriginal text}Kennedy Space Center is so crowded,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.21,1:32:09.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们听说进出几乎不可能\N{\rOriginal text}we're hearing it's nearly impossible to get in or out.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.38,1:32:15.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉 开慢点\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly, slow down.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.80,1:32:17.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}后面两位还好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Are you guys good back there?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.09,1:32:18.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很好 不好\N{\rOriginal text}Yes. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.60,1:32:22.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请别这样...\N{\rOriginal text}Please, please stop. Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.60,1:32:28.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}到了 就是这家店\N{\rOriginal text}There it is. There's the store.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.87,1:32:44.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 关门了\N{\rOriginal text}No! They're closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.21,1:32:47.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}关门了 什么?\N{\rOriginal text}They're closed. Oh, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.67,1:32:49.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不... 没关门\N{\rOriginal text}No, no. No, they are not.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.04,1:32:51.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly. Whoa, whoa, whoa. Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.21,1:32:53.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们还等什么呢? 快去\N{\rOriginal text}What are you waiting for? Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.55,1:32:55.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是... 好\N{\rOriginal text}Oh. Yeah, yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.09,1:32:57.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.18,1:33:00.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.26,1:33:01.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 这一台 很好 对 好\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, this one. This is great. Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.85,1:33:04.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我很想帮忙 只是我不够高 来吧 唐 好\N{\rOriginal text}I would help. I'm just not tall enough. Come on, Don. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.31,1:33:08.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 慢点 好的 各位 快点\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Slowly, all right. Guys, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.40,1:33:12.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 我可不能蹲监狱\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, my God. I can't go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.94,1:33:14.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}交给我\N{\rOriginal text}Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.94,1:33:14.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(警察)
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.66,1:33:28.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她真厉害\N{\rOriginal text}She's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.58,1:33:30.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是啊\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.71,1:34:16.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一路顺风 兄弟们\N{\rOriginal text}Have a good ride, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.22,1:34:23.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大约五分钟后\N{\rOriginal text}In a matter of, uh, five minutes or so
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.55,1:34:26.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们将看到飞船指挥官尼尔·阿姆斯特朗\N{\rOriginal text}we'll be ready for the spacecraft commander, Neil Armstrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.43,1:34:29.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跨过位于98米高空的舷门门槛\N{\rOriginal text}to come across the sill at the 320-foot level.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.49,1:34:47.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}搭乘穿梭面包车... 快啊\N{\rOriginal text}The trip in the transfer van... Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.37,1:34:50.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大约要15分钟才能抵达发射平台\N{\rOriginal text}Could take some 15 minutes or so to reach the pad.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.33,1:34:54.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}届时 宇航员将搭乘 两部电梯中先来的那部\N{\rOriginal text}At which time the astronauts will board, uh, the first of two elevators
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.46,1:34:58.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}前往发射平台所在的98米高空\N{\rOriginal text}for the trip to the 320-foot level at the launchpad,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.80,1:35:02.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}然后进入飞船\N{\rOriginal text}uh, where they will then proceed to ingress the spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.51,1:35:07.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}站住 已经准备就绪了 小伙子\N{\rOriginal text}Whoa. We are locked and loaded, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.97,1:35:09.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不... 飞行部要把这个放进飞船\N{\rOriginal text}No, no. Flight Deck wants this on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.44,1:35:15.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这里飞行部 放他过去 好\N{\rOriginal text}This is Flight Deck. Let him through. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.44,1:35:16.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}去吧\N{\rOriginal text}Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.48,1:35:21.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我们必须启动发射前的程序了 否则会错过窗口期\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, we need to initiate prelaunch, or we lose the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.99,1:35:23.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}给他一分钟就好\N{\rOriginal text}Just give him one minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.03,1:35:24.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}... 98米的高空\N{\rOriginal text}320-foot level,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.61,1:35:27.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}三位宇航员都已登上飞船\N{\rOriginal text}all three astronauts now aboard the spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.45,1:35:30.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}几分钟前 宇航员巴兹·奥尔德林 进来坐在了中间的位置\N{\rOriginal text}A few minutes ago, Astronaut Buzz Aldrin, uh, came in and took the center seat...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.87,1:35:35.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我听说船舱已经封闭 倒计时开始了\N{\rOriginal text}I'm hearing the cabin's now being sealed. Countdown has begun.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.46,1:35:38.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是他们发射时的姿态\N{\rOriginal text}These are the positions they will fly at liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.21,1:35:41.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}指挥官 这里是飞船测试员 听得清楚吗?\N{\rOriginal text}CDR, STC, how do you read?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.21,1:35:43.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飞船测试员 听得很清楚\N{\rOriginal text}STC, loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.09,1:35:45.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}早上好 尼尔 发射架已撤开\N{\rOriginal text}Good morning, Neil. Gantry is cleared.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.34,1:35:46.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}欢迎登船\N{\rOriginal text}Welcome aboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.51,1:35:49.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗11号准备发射 倒计时十分钟\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 11 is a go for launch in T-minus ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.60,1:35:51.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.81,1:35:56.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他回来了\N{\rOriginal text}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.90,1:35:58.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}接上了\N{\rOriginal text}It's connected.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.98,1:36:01.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}至少我认为接上了\N{\rOriginal text}At least I think I connected it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.82,1:36:04.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}斯图 什么意思?\N{\rOriginal text}Stu, what the hell does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.86,1:36:07.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只有几秒钟时间 没来得及进行压力测试 我...\N{\rOriginal text}I only had a few seconds. I didn't have time to stress test it. I...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.25,1:36:13.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 坐下吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.67,1:36:18.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 都听着\N{\rOriginal text}All right, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.97,1:36:26.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}无论今天这里发生什么\N{\rOriginal text}Whatever happens here today,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.43,1:36:29.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我都会支持你们做出的每一个决定\N{\rOriginal text}I will stand by every decision that you make.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.64,1:36:34.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}近十年来 超过四十万人参与了这项计划\N{\rOriginal text}Over 400,000 people have worked on this program for nearly ten years.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.02,1:36:36.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就为了实现一个人对全世界的承诺\N{\rOriginal text}All to keep one man's promise to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.73,1:36:38.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}让我们坚守这个承诺吧\N{\rOriginal text}So, let's keep it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.07,1:36:44.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 告诉我发射是否就绪吧\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Give me, "Go/No go" for launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.40,1:36:47.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}收到 所有岗位 准备进行最后的就绪核查\N{\rOriginal text}Ah, roger. All stations, stand by for final "Go/No go."
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.16,1:36:48.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}机械姿态电控 就绪\N{\rOriginal text}MACE. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.24,1:36:49.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}环境控制系统 就绪\N{\rOriginal text}ECS. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.62,1:36:51.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}电力系统 就绪\N{\rOriginal text}EPS. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.16,1:36:52.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}序列控制器 就绪\N{\rOriginal text}Sequencer. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.41,1:36:53.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}导航系统 就绪\N{\rOriginal text}GNS. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.66,1:36:56.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}航天器控制系统 这里最精彩了\N{\rOriginal text}SCS. This is the best part.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.29,1:36:59.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们依次问下去 每一个...\N{\rOriginal text}They go down the line and every single...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.04,1:37:02.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每一个技术员都必须说 发射“就绪”或“未就绪”\N{\rOriginal text}every single technician has to say, "Go," or, "No go," for launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.17,1:37:03.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}任何一人都能阻止发射\N{\rOriginal text}Any one of them can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.84,1:37:07.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}CFAT CSE 现在能回答“就绪”了吗?\N{\rOriginal text}CFAT. CSE, can you give me a "go" now?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.05,1:37:08.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}CSE就绪\N{\rOriginal text}CSE is go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.13,1:37:10.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 鹰号就绪\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Uh, Eagle is go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.78,1:37:27.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}CBTS 这里是CSA9号\N{\rOriginal text}CBTS, this is CSA 9.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.78,1:37:29.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}倒计时20秒\N{\rOriginal text}Twenty seconds and counting.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.20,1:37:34.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}倒计时15秒 制导系统已切换为自主模式\N{\rOriginal text}T-minus 15 seconds. Guidance is internal.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.70,1:37:39.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}十二 十一 十 九...\N{\rOriginal text}Twelve, eleven, ten, nine...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.46,1:37:43.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}点火程序启动\N{\rOriginal text}Ignition sequence starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.35,1:38:00.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}五 四 三 二 一\N{\rOriginal text}Five, four, three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.10,1:38:01.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所有引擎启动\N{\rOriginal text}All engines running.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.26,1:38:32.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}发射 火箭升空\N{\rOriginal text}Liftoff. We have liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.31,1:38:41.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}发射塔已分离\N{\rOriginal text}Tower clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.35,1:38:45.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}休斯敦 交给你了\N{\rOriginal text}Houston, she's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.64,1:39:59.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫·伯克斯来了 要找你们俩\N{\rOriginal text}Moe Berkus is here. For both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.60,1:40:02.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗11号已经升空\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 11 is on the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.48,1:40:04.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}四十万公里之外\N{\rOriginal text}250,000 miles away,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.56,1:40:08.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}月球在等待人类的首次到来\N{\rOriginal text}where the moon is waiting for man's first arrival.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.86,1:40:11.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}整个航程要用三天时间\N{\rOriginal text}Flight to take, uh, three days.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.07,1:40:14.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飞船要抵达...\N{\rOriginal text}And, uh, the, uh, spacecraft to reach there...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.53,1:40:16.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉全都告诉我了\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.78,1:40:21.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好极了\N{\rOriginal text}Bravissimo.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.37,1:40:23.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}省省吧 这是创造历史\N{\rOriginal text}Shove it. That was history.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.12,1:40:25.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 海伦 抱歉 是凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}Hi, Helen. Uh, sorry, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.37,1:40:28.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我听说你回来了 所以我也回来了\N{\rOriginal text}I heard you came back, so I came back too.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.67,1:40:34.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 去月球片场看了一眼\N{\rOriginal text}I... I took a little peeky-poo at the moon set,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.72,1:40:37.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真是完美\N{\rOriginal text}and it is perfection.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.01,1:40:39.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}干得好\N{\rOriginal text}Great job.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.01,1:40:42.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果你认为我会让你播出 这次任务的造假版本\N{\rOriginal text}If you think that I'm gonna let you broadcast some fake version of this,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.22,1:40:43.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那我现在就去找媒体\N{\rOriginal text}I'll go to the press right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.73,1:40:45.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科尔\N{\rOriginal text}Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.44,1:40:48.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科尔...\N{\rOriginal text}Cole. Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.19,1:40:56.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你... 去找媒体吧 带他们看看月球片场\N{\rOriginal text}You, uh... You go to the press. Bring 'em by the moon set,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.57,1:41:02.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但你要知道 今后再也不会有人相信国家航空航天局了\N{\rOriginal text}but just know that no one will ever trust the legitimacy of NASA again.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.54,1:41:05.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是国家安全问题\N{\rOriginal text}This is a matter of national security.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.54,1:41:08.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}本次直播必须在可控的情况下进行\N{\rOriginal text}This broadcast must take place in a controlled setting.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.79,1:41:11.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你应该最明白了\N{\rOriginal text}You of all people must understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.21,1:41:15.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}任务的重点已经不再是登月了\N{\rOriginal text}The mission isn't about landing on the moon anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.97,1:41:21.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而是全世界在电视上观看美国战胜苏联\N{\rOriginal text}It is about the world watching America beat Russia on TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.85,1:41:29.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我得赶飞机\N{\rOriginal text}I got a flight to catch.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.65,1:41:36.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我会及时赶回来看登月直播的\N{\rOriginal text}I'll be back in time for the lunar broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.15,1:41:37.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我想在这里看\N{\rOriginal text}I thought I'd watch it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.49,1:41:40.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉 和你一起在月球片场看\N{\rOriginal text}With you, Kelly. On the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.04,1:41:51.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 我们正在创造历史\N{\rOriginal text}Hey. We're making history.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.33,1:42:26.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你说我的那些话全都没错\N{\rOriginal text}Everything you said about me is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.70,1:42:28.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是个骗子 一直都是\N{\rOriginal text}I'm a con artist, and I always have been.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.87,1:42:33.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我的真名甚至不是凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}My real name is not even Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.84,1:42:38.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那些我跟你讲的故事\N{\rOriginal text}All those stories that I told you
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.38,1:42:40.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}说我和我妈挨家挨户推销\N{\rOriginal text}about my mom and I selling products door-to-door,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.68,1:42:41.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是真事\N{\rOriginal text}those were true.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.97,1:42:44.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但都是骗局\N{\rOriginal text}They were all scams.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.39,1:42:47.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们开始只是小打小闹 之后越做越大\N{\rOriginal text}And we started out small, and then they got bigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.43,1:42:51.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大到涉及地产和保险什么的\N{\rOriginal text}Like real estate and insurance.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.35,1:42:52.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}然后...\N{\rOriginal text}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.44,1:42:58.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我16岁那年 在北达科他州 有个人掏枪了\N{\rOriginal text}when I was 16, a guy in North Dakota pulled a gun
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.86,1:43:01.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我妈比他更快掏出枪 把他打死了\N{\rOriginal text}and my mom pulled hers out first and she killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.86,1:43:04.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她叫我逃跑 我照做了\N{\rOriginal text}And she told me to run and I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.53,1:43:07.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她进了监狱 我再也没见过她\N{\rOriginal text}And she went to prison and I never saw her again.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.96,1:43:15.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我伪造文件 用假名来找工作\N{\rOriginal text}And I forged documents and used fake names to get jobs.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.38,1:43:19.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我去纽约后发现了广告业\N{\rOriginal text}And when I went to New York, I found advertising.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.38,1:43:23.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就像我妈教我的骗局 但却合法\N{\rOriginal text}And that was like the scams that my mom taught me, but it was legal.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.39,1:43:29.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我骗了很多人\N{\rOriginal text}And I lied to so many people.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.35,1:43:32.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}最糟糕的谎言是我对自己说的那些\N{\rOriginal text}The worst lies were the ones I told myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.56,1:43:36.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}说所有人都在骗人 这只是一场大型游戏而已\N{\rOriginal text}That everybody does it. You know. It's just a big game.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.52,1:43:40.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但后来我来了这里\N{\rOriginal text}But then I came down here...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.45,1:43:44.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}认识了你\N{\rOriginal text}I met you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.24,1:43:52.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我了解到参与到真实事件中是什么感受\N{\rOriginal text}I learned what it was like to be a part of something real.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.67,1:43:58.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫提出的条件是抹去我的黑历史\N{\rOriginal text}Moe offered me a way to erase my past.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.96,1:44:00.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我原以为那就是我想要的 但...\N{\rOriginal text}I thought that's what I wanted, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.38,1:44:05.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不想再逃亡了\N{\rOriginal text}I don't wanna run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.02,1:44:16.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫是个值得尊敬的对手 但他遇到旗鼓相当的人了\N{\rOriginal text}Moe is a worthy opponent, but he has met his match.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.82,1:44:24.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我保证这是我最后一次 用欺骗的手段来获取我想要的东西\N{\rOriginal text}I promise this is the last time I will trick anyone into getting what I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.28,1:44:27.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我保证\N{\rOriginal text}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.74,1:44:31.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你觉得不撒谎也能做到吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you think you can do it without lying?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.62,1:44:35.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}绝对不行 好吧 我想也是\N{\rOriginal text}Absolutely not. Yeah, I didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.25,1:44:42.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那你有什么计划?\N{\rOriginal text}So, what's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.30,1:44:46.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们为什么在这里碰头?\N{\rOriginal text}Why are we meeting out here?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.18,1:44:49.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为莫监听一切对话 这人就像个魔术师 无处不在\N{\rOriginal text}Because Moe bugs everything. The guy's like Houdini. He's everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.80,1:44:52.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 莫不知道我们修好了登月舱摄像机\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, so, Moe doesn't know that we fixed the LEM camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.72,1:44:54.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们就此来制定计划\N{\rOriginal text}We build a plan around that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.18,1:44:57.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们只需让他相信我们在直播假登月\N{\rOriginal text}All we have to do is convince him that we are broadcasting the fake moon landing,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.90,1:45:00.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而实际上我们在播真的\N{\rOriginal text}when in reality we're broadcasting the real one.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.69,1:45:02.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们有没有办法给设备动手脚\N{\rOriginal text}Is there a way that we could rig the equipment
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.73,1:45:05.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}来播出真实的登月舱视频?\N{\rOriginal text}so that it actually sends out the real LEM video feed?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.24,1:45:07.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜托 两位\N{\rOriginal text}Come on, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.24,1:45:09.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们连登月都搞定了 给我个假设理论啊\N{\rOriginal text}You figured out how to land on the moon. Give me a hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.70,1:45:13.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 假设的话 我们可以重新接线\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, um, hypothetically, we could rewire it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.58,1:45:16.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}让设备只接收任务控制中心的播出信号\N{\rOriginal text}So that it only picks up the broadcast signal from Mission Control.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.25,1:45:18.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 然后和我们的信号同步 对\N{\rOriginal text}Sure, then sync it with our feed. Hmm. Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.17,1:45:25.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 各位\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.05,1:45:28.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫·伯克斯派这两位来测试播出信号\N{\rOriginal text}Moe Berkus sent these guys to test the broadcast feed.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.64,1:45:31.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫... 伯克斯 对 莫·伯克斯...\N{\rOriginal text}Moe... Moe Berk... Yes. Moe Berk... Moe Berkus.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.39,1:45:34.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们谁都没接到电话?\N{\rOriginal text}Telling me none of you got the phone call?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.10,1:45:37.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好极了 摄像机在哪?\N{\rOriginal text}Great. All right, where's the camera?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.23,1:45:42.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你还好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Are you okay? Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.44,1:45:44.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请你们快点好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Can you guys hurry up, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.94,1:45:47.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}唐 你把烟掐了吧\N{\rOriginal text}Don, maybe just take the cigarette out.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.99,1:45:50.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉... 我之前从没吸过烟\N{\rOriginal text}I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I've just never smoked a cigarette before.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.12,1:45:53.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不喜欢\N{\rOriginal text}I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.45,1:45:57.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}11号 这里是休斯敦\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, 11, this is Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.29,1:45:58.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}环月轨道进入就绪 完毕\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, you are go for LOI. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.50,1:46:00.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}确认 向月球前进\N{\rOriginal text}Confirmed. On track for the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.25,1:46:02.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波罗11号 这里是休斯敦\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 11, this is Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.13,1:46:04.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你的全部系统正常 要转到月球后面了\N{\rOriginal text}All your systems are looking good. Going around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.59,1:46:06.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们另一边见 完毕\N{\rOriginal text}We'll see you on the other side. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.13,1:46:08.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们失去了信号\N{\rOriginal text}And we've had loss of signal
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.05,1:46:10.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因为阿波罗11号飞到了月球后面\N{\rOriginal text}as Apollo 11 goes behind the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.18,1:46:14.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}现在是东部夏令时下午3点半\N{\rOriginal text}It's now 3:30 Eastern Daylight Time.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.51,1:46:18.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}3点46分时 我们应该能够收到 登月舱的第一个信号\N{\rOriginal text}At 3:46 we should be getting the first signal from the Lunar Module.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.69,1:46:21.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}估计观众有上亿人\N{\rOriginal text}The estimated audience: hundreds of millions.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.31,1:46:23.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可能有四亿人\N{\rOriginal text}Perhaps 400 million persons or so are watching
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.98,1:46:27.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}正在观看这一重大事件的直播...\N{\rOriginal text}this broadcast today of, uh, the greatest event...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.82,1:46:28.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}兄弟们\N{\rOriginal text}Boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.36,1:46:31.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 开始吧\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.79,1:46:42.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}再往下一点 很好 各位\N{\rOriginal text}A little bit more. Well done, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.75,1:46:50.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}伙计们 你们听到我说话 就当成是上帝的旨意\N{\rOriginal text}Boys, when you hear my voice, you hear God.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.80,1:46:52.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是个假月球\N{\rOriginal text}Now, this is a fake moon,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.22,1:46:54.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但对于全世界 这是真的 好戏上演了\N{\rOriginal text}but to the world, it's real. It's showtime, folks.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.10,1:46:55.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}必须... 记住我说到哪了\N{\rOriginal text}It needs to... Remember where I left off.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.64,1:46:59.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}政府感谢你们即将付出的努力\N{\rOriginal text}Your government thanks you for the work you're about to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.06,1:47:01.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别搞砸了\N{\rOriginal text}Now, don't fuck it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.77,1:47:04.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这破烂饮料为什么放这里?\N{\rOriginal text}What is this nasty shit doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.40,1:47:08.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 不好意思\N{\rOriginal text}God. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.40,1:47:10.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是本片场指定的汽水 这是我的椅子\N{\rOriginal text}This is a Tab set, and that is my chair.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.90,1:47:13.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉 处理一下 兰斯 非常感谢\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly, let's deal with this. Lance, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.28,1:47:15.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这些屏幕是我们的信号\N{\rOriginal text}So, these screens... This is our feed.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.33,1:47:17.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 然后...\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Okay. And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.79,1:47:20.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}电视是直播画面 好\N{\rOriginal text}And the TV's a live broadcast. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.46,1:47:21.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(阿波罗11号 月球直播)
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.42,1:47:23.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对\N{\rOriginal text}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.92,1:47:25.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}约瑟夫 我要坐下\N{\rOriginal text}Joseph, I'm sitting.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.34,1:47:27.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 你认真的?\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, my God. Are you real?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.05,1:47:29.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是导演 兰斯·瓦斯珀丁\N{\rOriginal text}I am the director, Lance Vespertine.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.92,1:47:33.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别碍事好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Stay out of my way, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.43,1:47:36.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我想说很高兴认识你 但到目前为止我不高兴\N{\rOriginal text}All right, I'd say it was nice to meet you, but so far, it is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.14,1:47:37.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}鸽子已经进笼\N{\rOriginal text}The pigeon's in the coop.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.89,1:47:39.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}收到\N{\rOriginal text}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.39,1:47:44.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 应该能收到了 休斯敦\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, you should have him now, Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.85,1:47:47.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}鹰号 我们有你的信号了 看起来不错 完毕\N{\rOriginal text}Eagle, we've got you now. It's looking good. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.32,1:47:53.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们从前窗就可以看到地球\N{\rOriginal text}We've got the Earth right out of our front window.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.36,1:47:55.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飞行指挥 我们准备着陆\N{\rOriginal text}Flight, we are go for landing.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.78,1:47:58.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}收到 明白 准备着陆 910米\N{\rOriginal text}Roger. Understand. Go for landing. 3,000 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.62,1:48:01.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}鹰号 状态很好 可以开始着陆\N{\rOriginal text}Eagle, looking great. You're go.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.22,1:48:17.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}位置检查显示 水平飞行距离有些过长\N{\rOriginal text}Position checks downrange show us to be a little long.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.97,1:48:20.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}430米 状态依然很好\N{\rOriginal text}1,400 feet. Still looking very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.31,1:48:23.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}P30 6加2.5\N{\rOriginal text}P30. Six plus two-five.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.23,1:48:24.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}看起来大约250米\N{\rOriginal text}Looks like about 820.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.81,1:48:26.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}降低引擎的功率\N{\rOriginal text}Throttle down.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.86,1:48:30.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飞行指挥 这里是鹰号\N{\rOriginal text}Flight, this is Eagle.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.11,1:48:34.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}宁静海里的石头比预期中多\N{\rOriginal text}Sea of Tranquility is rockier than expected.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.74,1:48:36.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们不得不再飞300米\N{\rOriginal text}We're gonna have to extend another thousand feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.82,1:48:38.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 兄弟们\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.49,1:48:41.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那样的话情况如何?\N{\rOriginal text}Where does that put us?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.62,1:48:43.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他们会剩下15秒的燃料 最好终止任务\N{\rOriginal text}It'll give 'em 15 seconds of fuel left. They're gonna wanna abort.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.79,1:48:46.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼尔能做到 只要放手让他飞即可\N{\rOriginal text}Neil can do this, they just gotta let him.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.75,1:48:48.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}待命 鹰号\N{\rOriginal text}Stand by, Eagle.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.75,1:48:48.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(燃料百分比)
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.42,1:48:51.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们正在计算延长飞行的耗油量\N{\rOriginal text}We are calculating what that will do to our fuel reserves.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.00,1:48:55.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}电气 环境和耗材主管计算 是15秒以内 准备终止任务\N{\rOriginal text}EECOM puts that within 15 seconds. Prepare for abort.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.55,1:48:57.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飞行指挥\N{\rOriginal text}Flight...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.89,1:49:01.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们曾在这个范围内 进行过成功测试 让他们着陆吧\N{\rOriginal text}we have run successful tests within that range. Let 'em land.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.98,1:49:05.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}30秒...\N{\rOriginal text}Thirty. Thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.52,1:49:07.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是骗人 你撒谎了\N{\rOriginal text}That's a lie. You lied.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.77,1:49:09.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我新学了几招 坐下\N{\rOriginal text}I've learned some new tricks. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.44,1:49:12.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 接下来只报告燃料数字\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, the only callouts from now on will be fuel.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.65,1:49:14.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}加油啊\N{\rOriginal text}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.57,1:49:17.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}鹰号 看起来不错 可以着陆\N{\rOriginal text}Eagle, looking great. You're go.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.99,1:49:20.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}430米 状态依然很好\N{\rOriginal text}1,400 feet. Still looking very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.54,1:49:24.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}107米 降速4\N{\rOriginal text}350 feet, down at four.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.20,1:49:27.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}30秒...\N{\rOriginal text}Thirty. Thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.08,1:49:28.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}降速2.5 前进\N{\rOriginal text}Down two and a half. Forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.25,1:49:31.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}前进 好 收到\N{\rOriginal text}Forward. Good. Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.09,1:49:34.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}前进速度11 正稳步下降\N{\rOriginal text}Eleven forward. Coming down nicely.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.84,1:49:36.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}61米 降速4.5\N{\rOriginal text}200 feet, four and a half down.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.59,1:49:39.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}降速5.5... 前进速度9\N{\rOriginal text}Five and a half down. Five and a half down, nine forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.30,1:49:40.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很好\N{\rOriginal text}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.82,1:49:53.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(月表接触)
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.03,1:49:55.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}接触灯亮了\N{\rOriginal text}Contact light.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.20,1:50:00.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}关闭引擎\N{\rOriginal text}Engine stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.88,1:50:14.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飞行指挥\N{\rOriginal text}Flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.71,1:50:17.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这里是宁静海基地\N{\rOriginal text}Tranquility Base here.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.88,1:50:19.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}鹰号已着陆\N{\rOriginal text}The Eagle has landed.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.10,1:50:28.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}收到 宁静海基地 地面收到\N{\rOriginal text}Roger, Tranquility, we copy on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.85,1:50:31.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有一群人脸都快憋青了\N{\rOriginal text}You got a bunch of guys about to turn blue.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.02,1:50:32.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们又能呼吸了 多谢\N{\rOriginal text}We're breathing again. Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.36,1:50:40.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}呼 老天\N{\rOriginal text}Whew. Boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.45,1:50:42.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们要忙一会儿了\N{\rOriginal text}We're going to be busy for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.08,1:50:47.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了... 可以了\N{\rOriginal text}All right, all right, all right. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.75,1:50:51.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}集中注意力 还没完呢\N{\rOriginal text}Let's focus. We're only halfway there.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.71,1:50:54.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 接下来交给我们 谢谢各位\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, we've got it from here. Thank you, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.63,1:50:57.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大家各就各位... 打起精神\N{\rOriginal text}Places. Places, everyone. Look sharp.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.71,1:50:58.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}打起精神来\N{\rOriginal text}Let's look sharp!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.97,1:51:01.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}爱德华... 走下舞台 真要命\N{\rOriginal text}Edvard, Edvard, off the stage. You're killing me.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.26,1:51:05.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}爱德华 完事了 停 你完工了 别再调整了\N{\rOriginal text}Edvard, we are done. Uh-uh. You're done. No more tweaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.18,1:51:07.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你是复读机吗? 我不是复读机\N{\rOriginal text}What are you, the repeater? No, I'm not the repeater.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.52,1:51:09.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是你来之前我们创立的系统\N{\rOriginal text}This is the system we created before you got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.82,1:51:18.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}已取下摄像机\N{\rOriginal text}Camera is coming down.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.12,1:51:25.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(直播中)
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.20,1:51:29.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}三 二 一 开拍\N{\rOriginal text}Three, two, one, and action.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.62,1:51:35.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}电视上有画面了\N{\rOriginal text}And we're getting a picture on the TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.13,1:51:37.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}画面还不错吧?\N{\rOriginal text}You got a good picture, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.96,1:51:40.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对比度很强烈\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, there's a great deal of contrast in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.84,1:51:42.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}收到 电视电路断路器已接通\N{\rOriginal text}Roger, TV circuit breaker's in,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.22,1:51:45.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}听得很清楚\N{\rOriginal text}and read you loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.39,1:51:48.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}收到\N{\rOriginal text}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.85,1:51:56.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 请确认一下\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Will you verify the position, uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.52,1:51:58.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}摄像机镜头的位置和光圈尺寸\N{\rOriginal text}the, uh, opening I ought to have on the camera?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.57,1:51:59.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}稍等\N{\rOriginal text}Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.86,1:52:02.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿姆斯特朗 准备下飞船\N{\rOriginal text}Armstrong, prepare to disembark.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.07,1:52:05.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}遮光面罩\N{\rOriginal text}Your visor.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.24,1:52:11.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要打开舱门出去了\N{\rOriginal text}I am opening the door for egress.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.35,1:52:34.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 尼尔 我们看到你正走下舷梯\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, Neil, we can see you coming down the ladder now.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.02,1:52:37.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 左脚\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, left.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.65,1:52:41.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}右脚\N{\rOriginal text}And right.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.78,1:52:46.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}左脚 右脚\N{\rOriginal text}Left and right.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.41,1:52:49.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 左脚下来...\N{\rOriginal text}Now, left foot off. Left foot off.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.08,1:52:52.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}慢点... 下来\N{\rOriginal text}Easy. Easy. Step down.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.20,1:52:55.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}落地\N{\rOriginal text}And land.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.87,1:52:58.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎么提前知道他要做什么?\N{\rOriginal text}How do you know what, uh, he's gonna do ahead of time?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.33,1:53:02.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}国家航空航天局全都排练过 凯莉借鉴了一下\N{\rOriginal text}NASA rehearsed all of this, and Kelly appropriated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.92,1:53:04.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就是偷嘛\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, stole it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.92,1:53:06.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我就知道我找对人了\N{\rOriginal text}I knew I hired the right people.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.93,1:53:09.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 来吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.01,1:53:12.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(真实信号 播出信号)
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.81,1:53:14.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天衣无缝 真难以置信\N{\rOriginal text}It's seamless. It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.02,1:53:18.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我来到舷梯底部了\N{\rOriginal text}I'm at the foot of the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.60,1:53:22.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}登月舱的支脚仅仅压进月球表面2到5厘米\N{\rOriginal text}The LEM footpads are only depressed in the surface about one or two inches,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.98,1:53:28.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不过靠近了看 月表的尘土似乎非常细腻\N{\rOriginal text}although the surface appears to be very, very fine-grained as you get close to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.61,1:53:33.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}几乎就像粉末 下面的尘埃非常细\N{\rOriginal text}It's almost like a powder. Down there, it's very fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.50,1:53:36.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要走下登月舱了\N{\rOriginal text}I'm gonna step off the LEM now.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.21,1:53:44.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是个人的一小步\N{\rOriginal text}That's one small step for man...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.30,1:53:51.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}却是人类的一大步\N{\rOriginal text}one giant leap for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.14,1:53:59.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这么精彩的话 我们可能得花好几年才想得出\N{\rOriginal text}We could have spent years coming up with something that good.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.69,1:54:02.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.90,1:54:05.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是剧本里的吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Was that, uh, in the script?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.57,1:54:07.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不是\N{\rOriginal text}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.36,1:54:09.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这句台词不错\N{\rOriginal text}That's a good line.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.54,1:54:17.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一级一级舷梯跳下来是很简单的\N{\rOriginal text}It's a very simple matter to hop down from one step to the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.41,1:54:20.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼尔要展示牌匾了\N{\rOriginal text}Neil is now unveiling the plaque.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.38,1:54:23.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}“地球的人类\N{\rOriginal text}"Here man, from the planet Earth,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.34,1:54:28.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}于公元1969年7月首次踏上月球\N{\rOriginal text}first set foot upon the moon, July 1969 AD.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.47,1:54:31.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们为全人类的和平而来”\N{\rOriginal text}We came in peace for all mankind."
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.06,1:54:35.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}准备好上镜了吗?\N{\rOriginal text}You ready for the camera?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.89,1:54:39.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼尔 这里是休斯敦 视野正常\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, Neil, this is Houston. The field of view is okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.31,1:54:42.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们希望你把摄像机对准右边一点 完毕\N{\rOriginal text}We'd like you to aim it a little bit more to the right. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.52,1:54:43.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.57,1:54:46.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}太往右了\N{\rOriginal text}Too much to the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.11,1:54:48.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}能往左4 5度吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Can you bring it back left about, uh, four or five degrees?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.62,1:54:55.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 看起来不错 尼尔\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. That looks good, Neil.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.91,1:54:59.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哥伦比亚号... 这里是休斯敦 接收信号 完毕\N{\rOriginal text}Columbia, Columbia, this is Houston, AOS. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.41,1:55:01.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼尔阿姆斯特朗目前已经在月球表面\N{\rOriginal text}Neil Armstrong has been on the lunar surface now
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.92,1:55:03.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}停留近45分钟了\N{\rOriginal text}almost 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.58,1:55:06.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}宁静海基地 这里是休斯敦\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, Tranquility Base, this is Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.00,1:55:08.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}请两位一起走进镜头一下好吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Could we get both of you on the camera for a minute, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.22,1:55:13.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}美国总统想跟你们说几句 完毕\N{\rOriginal text}The President of the United States would like to say a few words to you. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.26,1:55:15.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这是我们的荣幸\N{\rOriginal text}That would be an honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.68,1:55:17.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 总统先生 请讲吧\N{\rOriginal text}All right, go ahead, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.68,1:55:18.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这里是休斯敦 完毕\N{\rOriginal text}This is Houston. Out.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.77,1:55:20.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们好 尼尔和巴兹\N{\rOriginal text}Hello, Neil and Buzz.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.27,1:55:25.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我正在白宫的椭圆办公室 用电话跟你们通话\N{\rOriginal text}I am talking to you by telephone from the Oval Room at the White House...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.57,1:55:27.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这地方到处都是特勤局的人\N{\rOriginal text}They have Secret Service all over this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.73,1:55:31.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}这绝对是有史以来最重要的一次通话\N{\rOriginal text}And this certainly has to be the most historic telephone call ever made.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.32,1:55:34.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你们跟我们通话的同时...\N{\rOriginal text}And as you talk to us...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.95,1:55:37.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我觉得你跟他真的很像\N{\rOriginal text}He actually reminds me a lot of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.45,1:55:40.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别这么说 真的 连玩笑都别开\N{\rOriginal text}Do not say that. No, don't even joke about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.71,1:55:45.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}总统发表无聊讲话时我们要待命 别动\N{\rOriginal text}We're still holding while the president drones on. Don't move.
