Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.51,1:56:33.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我们不确定登月舱上的 摄像机是否运作正常\N{\rOriginal text}We're not sure that the camera on the LEM is working.
