Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.70,1:59:08.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 我知道你们都知道\N{\rOriginal text}Yes. I know you know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.50,1:59:10.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就是提醒一下大家我们今天在干什么\N{\rOriginal text}Just reminding everybody what we're doing here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.79,1:59:12.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是我们的人\N{\rOriginal text}Those are our guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.96,1:59:15.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大家继续忙吧\N{\rOriginal text}Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.22,1:59:22.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我看到的是什么?\N{\rOriginal text}What am I looking at here?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.89,1:59:24.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}月球\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, that's the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.26,1:59:27.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼尔 这里是休斯敦\N{\rOriginal text}Neil, this is Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.81,1:59:29.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你拿哈苏杂志...\N{\rOriginal text}Did you get the Hasselblad magazine...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.39,1:59:30.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真的是月球?\N{\rOriginal text}That's really the moon?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.64,1:59:34.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拿了 我们有大约...\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, I did. And we got about, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.23,1:59:36.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}老天 看起来好假 得有9公斤...\N{\rOriginal text}Jesus, it looks fake. I'd say 20 pounds of, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.94,1:59:40.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}精挑细选 但没有记录的样品\N{\rOriginal text}carefully selected, if not documented samples.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.65,1:59:43.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}休斯敦 收到 好样的 完毕\N{\rOriginal text}Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.07,1:59:48.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非官方时间 离开地面111小时37分32秒\N{\rOriginal text}Roger. Well done. Out. Unofficial time off the surface at 111:37:32.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.04,1:59:56.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我从没想过自己能这么近地看到月球\N{\rOriginal text}I never thought I would see the moon up close.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.63,1:59:57.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我也一样 沃尔特\N{\rOriginal text}Me neither, Walter.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.76,2:00:06.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我没搞定 天啊 抱歉\N{\rOriginal text}I didn't get it. Oh, my God. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.85,2:00:08.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}别和上次一样 不 别冲着我们开\N{\rOriginal text}Not like last time. No. Don't point it at us.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.52,2:00:11.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在波兰 我们说“na zdrowie”\N{\rOriginal text}In Polish, we call it "na zdrowie."
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.48,2:00:14.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 na zdrowie 好... 凯莉\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Na zdrowie. Okay, okay, okay. Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.10,2:00:15.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凯莉... 好点了\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly. Kelly. It's getting a little better.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:15.73,2:00:19.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什么事? 老天 说吧 就说一次\N{\rOriginal text}Yes? What? Christ, just say it. Just say it once.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.61,2:00:21.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你是我认识的最棒的导演\N{\rOriginal text}You are the best director I know.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.07,2:00:24.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的 好了 我知道此事要保密\N{\rOriginal text}I am. [inhales sharply] Now, I know we're not supposed to talk about this,
