Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.70,2:00:29.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}任何人把此事透露出去\N{\rOriginal text}Anyone mentions this to anyone,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.16,2:00:32.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就会在一个无名岛上阴暗的牢房里\N{\rOriginal text}you will spend the rest of your life in a dark, dank prison cell
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.66,2:00:34.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}度过余生\N{\rOriginal text}on a nameless island.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.88,2:00:38.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 为了配合香槟酒\N{\rOriginal text}Oh. Now, to wash down the bubbly,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.80,2:00:42.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我代表美国政府请大家喝苏格兰威士忌\N{\rOriginal text}on behalf of the US government, have a little, uh, scotch.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.63,2:00:44.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}爱德华\N{\rOriginal text}Hmm. Edvard.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:44.01,2:00:45.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我来一杯\N{\rOriginal text}I'll take one of those.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.22,2:00:48.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我做了一档价值十亿美元的电视节目 但观众只有一个人\N{\rOriginal text}I had a billion-dollar TV show for an audience of one.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.26,2:00:50.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}希望你看得开心\N{\rOriginal text}Hope you enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.31,2:00:53.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}干杯 这是一场完美的失败\N{\rOriginal text}Cheers. It was a perfect failure.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.06,2:00:55.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}对 干杯... 干杯\N{\rOriginal text}That's right. Cheers. Cheers. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:59.23,2:01:01.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}能聊几句吗?\N{\rOriginal text}Can I talk with you a moment?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.53,2:01:06.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}没有多少人违抗了我的命令\N{\rOriginal text}Not many people have gone against my orders
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.57,2:01:07.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}还能活命的\N{\rOriginal text}and lived to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.99,2:01:11.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不过话说回来 也没有多少人救过我\N{\rOriginal text}Then again, not many people have saved my ass.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.70,2:01:15.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}要解释月球上为什么有只猫 那可太难了\N{\rOriginal text}It would've been a real doozy to explain how the cat ended up on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.83,2:01:18.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你真是个美国英雄\N{\rOriginal text}You're a goddamn American hero.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.46,2:01:21.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}干得好\N{\rOriginal text}Great job.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:23.67,2:01:26.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 现在这里到处都是媒体\N{\rOriginal text}Now, this place is crawling with press.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.22,2:01:30.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}溅落之前 我们无法清理这里\N{\rOriginal text}So, uh, we can't really clear anything out until after splashdown.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:30.51,2:01:35.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在这期间呢 把一切和拍摄有关的文件全部销毁\N{\rOriginal text}In the meantime, shred any documents associated with the shoot.
